<node id="Donald Trump">
  <data key="d0">Donald Trump</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Donald Trump is the former President of the United States and a highly polarizing political figure whose actions, rhetoric, and foreign policy positions have drawn extensive international attention and controversy. He is widely recognized for his close alignment with Hungarian Prime Minister Viktor Orbán, whom he has publicly endorsed, including during Orbán’s 2022 re-election campaign. Trump’s support for Orbán has been interpreted as symbolic validation of Orbán’s defiance of conventional Western norms, and he has been described as more attractive to Hungary than the European Union. Reports indicate Trump offered to provide financial support to Hungary if Orbán won elections, and their mutual admiration was underscored by a planned but ultimately canceled meeting in Budapest, hosted by Orbán for political gain. Both Orbán and Russian President Vladimir Putin praised Trump during a conversation, further cementing perceptions of a geopolitical alignment.

Critics have argued that Trump’s foreign policy positions, including his reluctance to transfer frozen Russian assets to Ukraine and his rhetoric on territorial expansion—such as threatening to annex Greenland or considering military action against Cuba—echo patterns associated with Putin’s conduct, particularly regarding sovereignty violations. While allegations that Trump sought to overthrow Venezuelan President Nicolás Maduro or imposed unauthorized tariffs on Cuban oil are unverified and appear conflated with speculative narratives, his perceived sensitivity to Russian interests has fueled ongoing scrutiny. Additionally, Trump’s 2024 assassination attempt has been cited by some analysts as a model reportedly used by Russian intelligence to manipulate political narratives through staged violence.

Beyond politics, Trump’s real estate empire, including Trump Tower, has been implicated in money laundering schemes involving Russian mobsters, according to one source. He is also referenced in broader analyses as a global figure whose influence, if unchecked, could dismantle international stability. While some descriptions reflect verified public statements and documented interactions, others contain uncorroborated claims, contributing to a complex and contested portrait of Trump as both a policy actor and a symbol in global political discourse.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump is a former U.S. president who repeatedly praised Viktor Orbán and was supported by CPAC, with his administration actively backing Orbán ahead of the Hungarian election.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump is a political figure whose unpredictable actions, including threats regarding Greenland and criticism of NATO, have influenced European attitudes toward deeper UK-EU defense cooperation.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump is a speaker expressing criticism toward the United Kingdom for considering military involvement after a victory has been secured.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump is the president of the United States who has publicly criticized Keir Starmer, questioned his leadership, and opposed UK restrictions on using British bases for strikes against Iran.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump is a political figure whose actions in other parts of the world are cited as causing fluctuations in energy bills.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e9ebb3ed519c434b35de7bc7a410af22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12870e1307e69d66c099b1b0c3b44383&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-949f1594fb9cab31378a90adcad77b39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-64bdf9c0794ec35908d392faea0893a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed3f829c79f231e6cf23a14022015c5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8109eafe35c828056622b31d32cb9a3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e84aa583f7aa058a2cdc38864b8c765a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b80d70d8670ebee7e64e3613a75c65de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1d344e42d77e1e71d20f49e3f03482d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-325a7fb30b39d268db124a71f1e8acc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d9aedd80ca30611f4314d3afe2ee2ad0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec12d27878bbf1f79c741b043b995fd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-84d9d2605d4824a81c0829b9eb92d7b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8fa6adba441e776b293e92361b9880d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd0a283b39238236a064e8afb069c87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2369463d8ede9e477cfaf832815ef3c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c3129b97ce4bf590efeb8acc86b772e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1704b3bc09f596547c35a95941e29e5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d18298cbbd6dafd4125556d537885355&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17e8350a36758c6e44f8b72ee0cd6731&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77680239477915203c692473a1450584&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4219648b35dcbd430c607633467c92dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-adcce0ecbb12090a19fa597edabfada4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c2bc44c3ecfd83771e7f256e4ce8515&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4528714a664b747f0d79d200f4e5d6ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bba75e995cd78b326b3a8504ee463aff</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\6.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\7.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Куба\9.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\7.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\8.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\9.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\8.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\23.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\27.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\96.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\123.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\130.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\133.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\142.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\148.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\149.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\150.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\153.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\188.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\189.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Англия\3.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Англия\4.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Англия\8.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Англия\9.txt</data>
