<node id="730,000 barrels of oil">
  <data key="d0">730,000 barrels of oil</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">730,000 barrels of oil is the approximate quantity of Russian oil expected to be delivered to Cuba via a tanker. relation Russia 730,000 barrels of oil supply,shipment Russia is supplying approximately 730,000 barrels of oil to Cuba, as noted in the source text. relation 730,000 barrels of oil Cuba destination,delivery The 730,000 barrels of oil are expected to be delivered to Cuba, with arrival scheduled for March 31.</data>
