<node id="Vladimir">
  <data key="d0">Vladimir</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Vladimir is a person implied to be exempt from the tariff policy due to his friendship with Donald Trump, as suggested by the text. relation Donald Trump Vladimir exemption,preferential treatment The text implies that Vladimir, as a friend of Donald Trump, is exempt from the tariff policy enforced by Donald Trump.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-12870e1307e69d66c099b1b0c3b44383</data>
