  <data key="d2">Raúl Castro is the former leader of Cuba and the grandfather of Raúl Guillermo Rodríguez Castro, mentioned in the context of Cuban leadership. relation Raúl Guillermo Rodríguez Castro Raúl Castro family relationship,leadership lineage Raúl Guillermo Rodríguez Castro is the grandson of Raúl Castro, establishing a direct familial and political lineage within Cuban leadership.</data>
