<node id="United States Senate">
  <data key="d0">United States Senate</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">United States Senate is the legislative chamber where Republicans blocked a Democratic attempt to prevent Donald Trump from taking military action against Cuba without Congressional approval. entity Republicans in the United States Senate organization Republicans in the United States Senate is the correct canonicalized name for the entity previously labeled as "Республиканцы в Сенате США", which must be rendered in English as per system rules. entity Democrats organization Democrats is the correct canonicalized English name for the entity previously labeled as "Демократы", which must be rendered in English as per system rules. relation Republicans in the United States Senate Democrats blocked,opposition,political conflict Republicans in the United States Senate blocked the attempt by Democrats to prevent Donald Trump from taking military action against Cuba without Congressional approval. relation Donald Trump Cuba military action,target Donald Trump sought to undertake military action against Cuba without Congressional approval. relation Donald Trump Congress requirement,authorization Donald Trump aimed to take military action against Cuba without obtaining authorization from Congress.</data>
