<node id="Последний Капиталист">
  <data key="d0">Последний Капиталист</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Последний Капиталист is the publisher or content source of the video post containing the described campaign. entity MonoBase organization MonoBase is a partner or platform involved in the advertising collaboration for the video post. relation Последний Капиталист MonoBase advertising collaboration, content partnership Последний Капиталист and MonoBase are engaged in an advertising collaboration for the video post described in the source text. relation Последний Капиталист Greta Thunberg content publication, platform dissemination Последний Капиталист published a video post featuring Greta Thunberg’s campaign against the militarization of Europe. relation MonoBase Greta Thunberg content dissemination, platform support MonoBase, as a collaboration partner, facilitated the dissemination of the video post containing Greta Thunberg’s campaign.</data>
