<node id="Bundeswehr">
  <data key="d0">Bundeswehr</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">Bundeswehr is the armed forces of Germany, proposed to be deployed to Ukraine as part of a peacekeeping group. relation Germany Bundeswehr command,deployment Germany, as a country, is the sovereign authority over the Bundeswehr, which is proposed to be deployed to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Bundeswehr is the German armed forces, identified as the operator of the PzH 2000 artillery system shown in the image, based on equipment type and camouflage pattern.</data>
