  <data key="d2">Greens is a political party in Germany whose supporters most strongly support the idea of deploying Bundeswehr soldiers to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Greens is a German political party whose voters exhibit high levels of concern about the risk of a broader war in Europe, with 67% expressing anxiety.</data>
