  <data key="d2">Social Democrats is a political party in Germany whose supporters most strongly support the idea of deploying Bundeswehr soldiers to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Social Democrats are a centrist political group in the European Parliament that consistently voted against motions of censure against the European Commission.</data>
