<node id="Belousov">
  <data key="d0">Belousov</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Belousov is a Russian official who, alongside Vladimir Putin, outlined Russia’s military plans for 2026 through 2030, including sustaining offensive momentum, achieving SVO objectives, and preparing for potential conflict with NATO.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-965b8760e7f023cb5fe999d79e061c32</data>
