<node id="Special Military Operation (SVO)">
  <data key="d0">Special Military Operation (SVO)</data>
  <data key="d1">conflict</data>
  <data key="d2">The Special Military Operation (SVO) is Russia’s term for its military campaign in Ukraine, with objectives extending beyond Donbas to include Sumy and Kharkiv, and aimed at securing what Russia calls its “historical lands.”</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-965b8760e7f023cb5fe999d79e061c32</data>
