<node id="Ministry of Defense of Russia">
  <data key="d0">Ministry of Defense of Russia</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Ministry of Defense of Russia is the Russian government body where Vladimir Putin and Belousov presented military plans for 2026–2030 during a college meeting. relation Vladimir Putin Ministry of Defense of Russia leadership, official meeting Vladimir Putin participated in a meeting of the Ministry of Defense of Russia, where he and Belousov announced Russia’s military plans for 2026–2030. relation Belousov Ministry of Defense of Russia leadership, official meeting Belousov, as a Russian official, participated in a meeting of the Ministry of Defense of Russia alongside Vladimir Putin to present military plans for 2026–2030.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ministry of Defense of Russia produced a classified document detailing reconnaissance operations using UAVs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-965b8760e7f023cb5fe999d79e061c32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bea54a7e2da99c4d21fe120e09b5930</data>
