<node id="Iran">
  <data key="d0">Iran</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Iran is a country where hundreds of Greta Thunberg's peers are being killed, and where Western leftists and media have remained silent.&lt;SEP&gt;Iran is a country that received an offer of assistance from the Hungarian government after the September 2024 pager attack, and whose foreign minister engaged in discussions with Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Iran is a country that is the target of strikes conducted by B-1B Lancer bombers.&lt;SEP&gt;Iran is the country at the center of the security conflict between the United States and the United Kingdom, with the U.S. seeking to conduct military strikes and the U.K. refusing to permit initial attacks from its territory.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19a6a792a17fb2ca480328851eba5ff4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6f7b78146485b6ecfc5184d01e665fc8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b045b789bd2de98a3423aae473a1a2e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4528714a664b747f0d79d200f4e5d6ef</data>
