<node id="Resurgam">
  <data key="d0">Resurgam</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Resurgam is an organization that publishes articles on its website resurgamhub, covering topics such as financial crises, geopolitics, and energy policy in Eastern Europe.&lt;SEP&gt;Resurgam is a user or entity inviting others to join, as indicated by the text "Присоединяйся".&lt;SEP&gt;Resurgam is a Ukrainian ultra-radical propaganda platform on YouTube, founded by Dmytro Korniienko, which published a video involving a sword and became the subject of Hungarian disinformation claims.&lt;SEP&gt;Resurgam is a term or entity associated with a call to join, as indicated in the input text.</data>
