  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Молдова is a country undergoing large-scale energy system modernization to exit Russian energy dependence.&lt;SEP&gt;Молдова is a country where Russian operatives, under Sergei Kirienko's command, previously managed voter-buying networks, troll farms, and offline influence campaigns against President Maia Sandu.</data>
