<node id="Виктор Орбан">
  <data key="d0">Виктор Орбан</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Виктор Орбан is the long-term leader of Hungary who faces a real threat of losing power, with consequences affecting both Moscow and Washington.&lt;SEP&gt;Виктор Орбан is the Prime Minister of Hungary and the political figure targeted for preservation in power by the Russian operation.</data>
