<node id="Венгрия">
  <data key="d0">Венгрия</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Венгрия is a country in Central Europe led by Prime Minister Viktor Orbán, whose political leadership has significantly influenced its domestic and geopolitical trajectory. Orbán’s government, associated with the political party Fidesz, has been the target of a covert Russian influence operation known as «Будапешт», which aimed to preserve his hold on power ahead of parliamentary elections by manipulating political outcomes. This operation involved the deployment of a three-person team to Budapest under diplomatic cover. While recent elections saw the highest voter turnout in three decades, both Fidesz and Orbán experienced less favorable results than in prior contests, indicating shifting public sentiment.

Vengria’s political environment has also drawn international attention due to its alignment with Russian interests and its role as a source of anti-Ukrainian propaganda, which has been formally countered by the Ukrainian Ministry of Foreign Affairs. The country’s national security has been cited in legislative discussions concerning the assets of Oshchadbank, reflecting its involvement in broader regional financial and political tensions. Historically, Hungary experienced high crime rates in the 1990s, leading to government crackdowns tied to figures such as Шандор Пинтер, Магилевич, and Игорь Король, with legal proceedings and imprisonments occurring within its judicial system.

Additionally, Hungary is the country where Alexander Kirichanin has resided since 1994 and where a violent assault took place, underscoring its role in personal and criminal narratives beyond state-level politics. Despite internal political challenges and external interference, Hungary remains a focal point of geopolitical competition between Russia and the United States, with its elections, governance, and security policies continuously shaping regional dynamics.&lt;SEP&gt;Венгрия is a country labeled as "недружественной страной" (unfriendly country) by Песков.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64bdf9c0794ec35908d392faea0893a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-769ff8feb3b00c3c503fb9e86e9bdf0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b27aeca6858b7e54f862c47192fbcea2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85ab176e3cbddf97c2d5cd15191ff861&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f70e0895097bbb48ff32f2b973c6e11&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07b6315bf58723ab4516f38303c600bf</data>
