<node id="Диана Лебедь">
  <data key="d0">Диана Лебедь</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Диана Лебедь is a Moldovan politics analyst and author of the Telegram channel "Винная политика," who wrote an article for Resurgam on Moldova’s energy strategy. entity Константин Глушко person Константин Глушко is an analyst and columnist for Resurgam’s Center on Northern European politics, who authored articles on Donald Trump’s interest in Greenland and Sweden’s intelligence upgrades. entity resurgamhub organization resurgamhub is the website operated by Resurgam, where articles are published on geopolitical and economic topics; its name appears in lowercase in the source text but refers to the same organization as Resurgamhub. entity Соединённые Штаты country Соединённые Штаты is the country that detained two Russian shadow fleet tankers and conducted operations against Venezuela, impacting Russian interests. relation Диана Лебедь Resurgam authorship, content contribution Диана Лебедь authored an article for Resurgam on Moldova’s energy system modernization and its role in reducing Russian energy dependence. relation Константин Глушко Resurgam authorship, content contribution Константин Глушко authored two articles for Resurgam on Donald Trump’s interest in Greenland and Sweden’s acquisition of radar satellites. relation Соединённые Штаты Bella 1 operational seizure, enforcement action Соединённые Штаты detained the Bella 1 tanker as part of an operation targeting the Russian shadow fleet, formally framed as enforcement against Venezuela. relation Соединённые Штаты Sophia operational seizure, enforcement action Соединённые Штаты detained the Sophia tanker as part of an operation targeting the Russian shadow fleet, formally framed as enforcement against Venezuela. relation resurgamhub Диана Лебедь content publication, platform hosting resurgamhub published an article authored by Диана Лебедь on Moldova’s energy strategy. relation resurgamhub Константин Глушко content publication, platform hosting resurgamhub published articles authored by Константин Глушко on Greenland and Sweden’s intelligence capabilities. relation Соединённые Штаты Kremlin geopolitical confrontation, strategic rivalry Соединённые Штаты’ seizure of Russian shadow fleet tankers provoked Кремль’s intervention, escalating strategic rivalry between the two.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-64bdf9c0794ec35908d392faea0893a5</data>
