<node id="Алиса Вайдель">
  <data key="d0">Алиса Вайдель</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Алиса Вайдель is the leader of the German right-wing party AfD, who criticized double standards in international law violations by Vladimir Putin and Donald Trump. entity AfD organization AfD is a German right-wing political party led by Алиса Вайдель. entity Vladimir Putin person Vladimir Putin is a political figure accused by Алиса Вайдель of violating international law. entity Donald Trump person Donald Trump is a political figure accused by Алиса Вайдель of violating the sovereignty of Venezuela and Greenland, mirroring actions previously attributed to Vladimir Putin. entity Venezuela country Venezuela is a country whose sovereignty is alleged to have been violated by Donald Trump, according to Алиса Вайдель. entity Greenland location Greenland is a territory whose sovereignty is alleged to have been violated by Donald Trump, according to Алиса Вайдель. relation Алиса Вайдель AfD leadership,political affiliation Алиса Вайдель is the leader of the German right-wing party AfD. relation Алиса Вайдель Vladimir Putin criticism,international law violation Алиса Вайдель criticized Vladimir Putin for violating international law, citing past public outrage over his actions. relation Алиса Вайдель Donald Trump criticism,international law violation Алиса Вайдель accused Donald Trump of committing the same international law violations - specifically, violating the sovereignty of Venezuela and Greenland - that were previously condemned in Vladimir Putin's actions. relation Donald Trump Venezuela sovereignty violation,international intervention According to Алиса Вайдель, Donald Trump violated the sovereignty of Venezuela, drawing a parallel to actions attributed to Vladimir Putin. relation Donald Trump Greenland sovereignty violation,international intervention According to Алиса Вайдель, Donald Trump violated the sovereignty of Greenland, drawing a parallel to actions attributed to Vladimir Putin.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed3f829c79f231e6cf23a14022015c5c</data>
