<node id="Greenland">
  <data key="d0">Greenland</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Greenland is a territory whose sovereignty is alleged to have been violated by Donald Trump, according to Алиса Вайдель.&lt;SEP&gt;Greenland is a territory that Donald Trump threatened to annex, and which is the subject of geopolitical analysis in the context of European far-right parties.&lt;SEP&gt;Greenland is a territory referenced in Donald Trump’s threats, which contributed to shifting European perceptions of U.S. reliability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ed3f829c79f231e6cf23a14022015c5c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8109eafe35c828056622b31d32cb9a3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-adcce0ecbb12090a19fa597edabfada4</data>
