<node id="France">
  <data key="d0">France</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">France is a European country where far-right parties are closely aligned with Russia and have been compelled to criticize Donald Trump to avoid association with his aggressive policies.&lt;SEP&gt;France is a NATO member state that operates the Falcon 8X Archange aircraft for signals intelligence.&lt;SEP&gt;France is a European Union member state whose advisors have attempted to initiate talks with Russia, and whose president, Macron, supports eventual negotiations with Russia under appropriate conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;France is a European country led by Emmanuel Macron, with whom Keir Starmer coordinates on defense and security strategy.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8109eafe35c828056622b31d32cb9a3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d8dc136c80cd91ef2cf9ad9756a4d52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3117b3a03ff471f00f67b26aade3e091&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-adcce0ecbb12090a19fa597edabfada4</data>
