<node id="Bloomberg">
  <data key="d0">Bloomberg</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Bloomberg is a media organization that published an article and provided the photograph illustrating the geopolitical context of Donald Trump’s interest in Greenland.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg published satellite imagery from Planet Labs showing the empty storage tank at Brody and reported on the Russian strike’s impact.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is the news source that reported on the mass protest in Budapest against Viktor Orbán’s policies. relation Bloomberg Viktor Orbán media reporting,political coverage Bloomberg reported on Viktor Orbán’s policies and the resulting mass protests in Budapest. relation Bloomberg Péter Márki-Zay media reporting,political coverage Bloomberg reported on Péter Márki-Zay as the opposition leader whose supporters participated in the protests against Viktor Orbán. relation Bloomberg Hungary media reporting,geopolitical coverage Bloomberg reported on the political division in Hungary, including protests and the competing rallies during the 1848 Revolution anniversary.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is an organization that published a recording of a phone conversation between Orbán and Putin.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is a media organization that obtained and published the transcript of Orbán’s phone call with the Kremlin.&lt;SEP&gt;Bloomberg is a media outlet that published a report on military assistance from Северная Корея to Russia.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8109eafe35c828056622b31d32cb9a3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-141360bcc1e8268affe7476ca1b210ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-443c22f60ed93ec379e718efa356a140&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec12d27878bbf1f79c741b043b995fd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd0a283b39238236a064e8afb069c87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f525f78f89f5b96d8fc7535b3303ae6b</data>
