<node id="European far-right parties">
  <data key="d0">European far-right parties</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">European far-right parties are political groups in Germany, France, and Slovakia that have reassessed their ties to Donald Trump due to his aggressive policies, including threats to annex Greenland and military intervention in Venezuela.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8109eafe35c828056622b31d32cb9a3b</data>
