<node id="Alexander Dugin">
  <data key="d0">Alexander Dugin</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alexander Dugin is the main ideologist of the "Russian world" who expressed the view that sovereign states like Armenia, Azerbaijan, Kazakhstan, Georgia, and Uzbekistan must either join a unified union or become a platform for the United States and the European Union.</data>
