  <data key="d2">Russian World is an ideological concept associated with Alexander Dugin, advocating for a unified political and cultural sphere encompassing former Soviet states. relation Alexander Dugin Russian World ideological leadership, association Alexander Dugin is identified as the main ideologist of the Russian World, indicating a direct ideological association.</data>
