  <data key="d0">PzH 2000</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">PzH 2000 is a German self-propelled howitzer artillery system observed in a forested, muddy environment, likely during winter, and associated with German military operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9ed06713c000461ec66858856eef1a63</data>
