<node id="Poland">
  <data key="d0">Poland</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Poland is a NATO member country that has significantly strengthened its national defense in response to regional security threats, particularly following Russia’s invasion of Ukraine. In 2024, Poland allocated approximately $2 billion to the “Eastern Shield” project, which involves constructing fortifications, bunkers, and anti-tank ditches along its borders with Russia and Belarus. As a key transit state, Poland is connected to Lithuania via the strategically vital Suwałki Corridor, a route that analysts believe Russia may seek to disrupt in order to isolate the Baltic States. German respondents have identified Poland as a potential target of Russian aggression, underscoring its frontline role in Eastern European security. Poland’s military contributions extend beyond its borders: its fighter jets now assist in defending Slovak airspace following the transfer of its MiG-29s to Ukraine. Domestically, Poland has reduced its energy dependence on Russia, resulting in relatively lower fuel prices compared to neighboring states. Politically, Poland has taken a firm stance in support of Ukraine, with Foreign Minister Sikorski publicly criticizing Hungary’s position on the conflict. Prime Minister Donald Tusk has also been vocal in condemning policies perceived as undermining Ukraine’s sovereignty. Additionally, Poland is currently analyzing a request from Slovakia to permit airspace transit for Slovak Prime Minister Robert Fico’s planned flight to Moscow, reflecting the complex diplomatic balancing act within the region.&lt;SEP&gt;Poland is a neighboring country to Slovakia that Robert Fico approached for airspace transit after being denied by the Baltic states.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9ed06713c000461ec66858856eef1a63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fa2b47c359e22a6528975dcd5b3e91a6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a126839f1ff6597735159d84aa24a61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0db27d1e5bd672959a82744488e5a07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1d38d0ea892917e129f8c929d603be9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69564d3bce60628ec150d14cc9a006c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9360bf859acb934b8ebad024d1c18290&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81f9a312226a282bf8ebf1aee5ad788a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9bcca043358a8f1b8a9a2999a79a6f6</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\12.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Балтийские страны\3.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Балтийские страны\6.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\13.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\28.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\29.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\136.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\197.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\198.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777938035</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Lithuania">
  <data key="d0">Lithuania</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Lithuania is a NATO member country identified by German respondents as a potential target of Russian aggression following the conflict in Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Lithuania is a Baltic State connected to Poland via the Suwałki Corridor, which Russia may target to isolate the Baltic States.&lt;SEP&gt;Lithuania is a country that refused to allow Robert Fico's plane to fly over its territory en route to Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Lithuania is a Baltic country that denied Robert Fico permission to fly through its territory to reach Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Lithuania is a Baltic nation that refused to allow Robert Fico’s aircraft to transit its airspace, signaling opposition to his pro-Kremlin overtures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9ed06713c000461ec66858856eef1a63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a126839f1ff6597735159d84aa24a61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-313fbd5b1968d3d281c042524d458b06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81f9a312226a282bf8ebf1aee5ad788a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9bcca043358a8f1b8a9a2999a79a6f6</data>
