</node>
<node id="Alice Weidel">
  <data key="d0">Alice Weidel</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alice Weidel is a prominent AfD politician and close ally of Markus Frömmel.&lt;SEP&gt;Alice Weidel is co-leader of the Alternative for Germany (AfD) party and a member of the Bundestag, who publicly supported Viktor Orbán and Fidesz.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b328e8d4304c0d0b1c17749a4f9e42bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aeeb3e654a660cb7b38dfc9d61222bc9</data>
