<node id="Politico">
  <data key="d0">Politico</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">POLITICO is an organization that received a statement from Зеленский.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico is a media organization that reported suspicions regarding AfD's transmission of classified European Union documents to Russia. relation AfD Politico reporting,media coverage Politico reported the suspicions that AfD transmitted classified European Union documents to Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico is an organization that reported on the exclusion of Hungary from sensitive European Union discussions.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico is a news publication that reported the European Union had already excluded Hungary from official activities but delayed formal accusations until after Hungarian elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico is the publication that authored the article discussing Viktor Orban's political alignment with Vladimir Putin. relation Viktor Orban Politico media coverage, journalistic focus The article published by Politico provides an in-depth analysis of Viktor Orban's political evolution and his alliance with Vladimir Putin, making it the source of the described content.&lt;SEP&gt;Politico is a media outlet that obtained and published documents detailing the 12-point cooperation agreement between Hungary and Russia.</data>
