<node id="Ursula von der Leyen">
  <data key="d0">Ursula von der Leyen</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Ursula von der Leyen is the President of the European Commission and a representative of the center-right European People's Party. She is a central figure in European political establishment and has been the target of multiple votes of no confidence in 2025 from both far-right and far-left factions in the European Parliament.&lt;SEP&gt;Ursula von der Leyen is the president of the European Commission who faced multiple motions of censure between 2025 and 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;Ursula von der Leyen is a leader of the European Union who is quoted in the petition as saying Europe must fight.&lt;SEP&gt;Ursula von der Leyen is a political leader who issued a joint statement with Antonio Costa regarding the plan to repair the "Druzhba" pipeline and unlock funds for Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Ursula von der Leyen is the President of the European Commission, referenced in a deepfake video involving Peter Magyar, where he falsely claims to choose the "left path" away from war and high taxes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8f1d70c706294695eca41aa0252d062&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a73e41ce47973ce6d0501f8f7acc0955&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1cf1470bc49240f9597eaaea1f12646e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9d4541f93fbe1abbecc6f52128db7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95251bcfc4d08a0a36c341b9a9e2da54</data>
