</node>
<node id="European People's Party">
  <data key="d0">European People's Party</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The European People's Party is a center-right political party in the European Union, of which Ursula von der Leyen is a representative.&lt;SEP&gt;European People's Party is a centrist political group in the European Parliament that consistently voted against motions of censure against the European Commission.&lt;SEP&gt;The European People's Party is the political party to which Weber belongs, as mentioned in the context of a hypothetical conversation with Madjar.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8f1d70c706294695eca41aa0252d062&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a73e41ce47973ce6d0501f8f7acc0955&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce845ea082895ffef253ac499ba46794</data>
