<node id="Patriots for Europe">
  <data key="d0">Patriots for Europe</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Patriots for Europe is a far-right political faction in the European Parliament that criticizes Ursula von der Leyen for promoting globalization and undermining national sovereignty.&lt;SEP&gt;Patriots for Europe (PfE) is a political group in the European Parliament that initiated two motions of censure in October 2025 and January 2026 against the European Commission.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8f1d70c706294695eca41aa0252d062&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a73e41ce47973ce6d0501f8f7acc0955</data>
