<node id="Green Deal">
  <data key="d0">Green Deal</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Green Deal is Ursula von der Leyen’s flagship policy initiative aimed at making the European Union climate-neutral, which has drawn criticism from both far-right and far-left factions for different reasons.</data>
