<node id="Pfizergate">
  <data key="d0">Pfizergate</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Pfizergate is a scandal involving opaque multibillion-euro COVID-19 vaccine procurement deals conducted through private SMS messages between Ursula von der Leyen’s administration and the CEO of Pfizer.&lt;SEP&gt;Pfizergate is a political scandal in 2025 involving allegations of opacity in COVID-19 vaccine procurement and demands for Ursula von der Leyen to release her private SMS correspondence with the CEO of Pfizer.</data>
