<node id="Israel">
  <data key="d0">Israel</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Israel is a country whose military actions in the Gaza Strip have been fully supported by Ursula von der Leyen, drawing strong criticism from far-left factions in the European Parliament.&lt;SEP&gt;Israel is a country whose partners are engaged in diplomatic discussions by the Hungarian Minister of Foreign Affairs outside European Union meetings.&lt;SEP&gt;Israel conducted a deadly attack in September 2024 that resulted in the detonation of thousands of Hezbollah pagers.&lt;SEP&gt;Israel is mentioned as engaging in a war against Iran alongside the United States, contributing to regional instability and rising energy prices.</data>
