<node id="European Parliament">
  <data key="d0">European Parliament</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The European Parliament is the legislative body of the European Union where far-right and far-left factions initiated votes of no confidence against Ursula von der Leyen in 2025. relation Ursula von der Leyen European Parliament target,criticism Ursula von der Leyen was the target of multiple votes of no confidence initiated by far-right and far-left factions within the European Parliament in 2025. relation Patriots for Europe European Parliament membership,affiliation Patriots for Europe is a far-right political faction within the European Parliament that criticizes Ursula von der Leyen. relation The Left European Parliament membership,affiliation The Left is a far-left political faction within the European Parliament that criticizes Ursula von der Leyen. relation Green Deal European Union policy,initiative The Green Deal is a policy initiative of the European Union under Ursula von der Leyen’s leadership aimed at achieving climate neutrality. relation Pfizergate European Commission scandal,controversy Pfizergate is a scandal involving the European Commission under Ursula von der Leyen’s leadership due to opaque vaccine procurement deals with Pfizer.&lt;SEP&gt;European Parliament is the legislative body of the European Union where motions of censure against the European Commission are voted upon.&lt;SEP&gt;European Parliament is the legislative body of the European Union where Viktor Orbán, Fidesz, and their international allies, including Meloni, Weidel, and Le Pen, share ideological alignment.&lt;SEP&gt;The European Parliament is criticized for rewarding "green" initiatives while supporting Ukraine financially despite its actions against European energy security.&lt;SEP&gt;The European Parliament is an institution of the European Union that raised accusations against Hungary of spying for Russia in January 2025.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e8f1d70c706294695eca41aa0252d062&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a73e41ce47973ce6d0501f8f7acc0955&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-aeeb3e654a660cb7b38dfc9d61222bc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-204b60f8b5f56bb209e8ca6cc9af48f9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a810084503e65cb067ff1fc3c7a05189</data>
