<node id="Brussels">
  <data key="d0">Brussels</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Brussels is the de facto capital of the European Union and the seat of its principal institutions, including the European Commission and the European Parliament, which are headquartered there. It functions as the administrative and political center of EU bureaucracy, drawing both institutional authority and political controversy. In January 2026, Brussels was criticized in a motion of censure for excessive centralization of power, a sentiment echoed by Hungarian Prime Minister Viktor Orbán, who rhetorically portrays Brussels as a new imperial dictator replacing Moscow. Orbán and his media apparatus have repeatedly accused Brussels of undermining Hungary’s energy independence, manipulating consumer prices, controlling information available to Hungarian voters, and interfering in Hungary’s electoral processes. These accusations extend to claims that Brussels disregards the interests of European taxpayers by favoring Ukraine and failing to lift sanctions on Russian oil. Brussels is also depicted in disinformation campaigns as a symbolic center of external influence over Hungarian political figures such as Péter Márki-Zay and László Mádiár, with the latter’s prior employment at the Hungarian Ministry of Foreign Affairs in Brussels being falsely framed as evidence of foreign control. Despite these criticisms, Brussels remains a pivotal node in EU governance, its future shaped significantly by Hungary’s blocking actions and Orbán’s broader policy resistance. Conflicting portrayals of Brussels—as both an administrative hub and a coercive imperial entity—reflect deepening political tensions between EU institutions and nationalist governments, particularly in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a73e41ce47973ce6d0501f8f7acc0955&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1cf1470bc49240f9597eaaea1f12646e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c1d344e42d77e1e71d20f49e3f03482d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3960e17c128f750dfd948945c91a00ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f3dc55aad4eb94544269bbfd9dec2905&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-effd94d17758c91a975ace308b74d363&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49d9496e943d94ccc071cf105396b990&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd0a283b39238236a064e8afb069c87</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Ультра левые и ультра правые\21.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\7.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\27.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\59.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\72.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\110.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\129.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936518</data>
