  <data key="d0">Al-Qaeda</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Al-Qaeda is a jihadist organization supported by Atomwaffen Division and referenced as a shared ideological enemy of liberal democracies within the Terrorgram scene.&lt;SEP&gt;Al-Qaeda is an Islamist terrorist organization that was allegedly financed by the bank Al-Taqwa and associated with extremist networks linked to Nazi converts.&lt;SEP&gt;Al-Qaeda is a terrorist organization that, according to the FBI, received weapons from Semen Mogilevich’s organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bdde8f24aa613c9ae76329db019d6d7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c0e45973e2056f2a0c6c6cf9df17553&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
