  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Albert Friedrich Huber was a Swiss banker who adopted Islam, owned the bank Al-Taqwa, which was accused of financing Osama bin Laden and Al-Qaeda, and held Nazi ideological views.</data>
