  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">David Myatt was a British neo-Nazi and Islamist who authored extremist texts justifying martyrdom operations, including "A Practical Guide to Aryan Revolution" and "Are Martyrdom Operations Lawful According to the Qur’an and Sunnah?", and was cited by both Aryan Nations and Hamas.</data>
