  <data key="d1">conflict</data>
  <data key="d2">white jihad is a radical ideological movement that synthesizes neo-Nazi and white supremacist ideologies with elements of radical Islamic discourse and accelerationist militancy.&lt;SEP&gt;White Jihad refers to the phenomenon of white supremacists and neo-Nazis adopting Islamist terminology, symbolism, and tactics, forming a fused extremist ideology with jihadist groups.</data>
