<node id="Ultraright Anti-Ukrainian Forces">
  <data key="d0">Ultraright Anti-Ukrainian Forces</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Ultraright Anti-Ukrainian Forces are political forces aligned with Robert Fico in a coalition, whose position he is compelled to consider.</data>
