  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Belarus is a country sharing a border with Poland, against which fortifications of the "Eastern Shield" project are also directed.&lt;SEP&gt;Belarus is a country through which Russia may channel migrant pressure as part of hybrid warfare against the Baltic States and Europe.&lt;SEP&gt;Belarus is a country cited as a clear example of long-term Russian influence that has been difficult to reverse.</data>
