  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alexander Arutyunyan, known by the pseudonym "Razvedos," is a Russian military blogger, veteran of the Russian-Chechen war, and military instructor who provides critical analysis of the Russian military’s capabilities and strategic overestimations.</data>
