<node id="CNC machines">
  <data key="d0">CNC machines</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">CNC machines are equipment located at Russian defense enterprises, which can be disabled by blocking software updates. entity Российские оборонные предприятия other Russian defense enterprises are facilities where CNC machines are operated and targeted for information gathering. relation CNC machines Российские оборонные предприятия location, equipment deployment CNC machines are located at Russian defense enterprises, as referenced in the speaker’s request for information. relation speaker CNC machines target, operational disruption The speaker seeks to disable CNC machines by blocking their software updates, indicating a strategic interest in their operational integrity. relation speaker Российские оборонные предприятия intelligence target, information source The speaker explicitly seeks information about Russian defense enterprises, making them a direct target of intelligence collection.</data>
