<node id="Latvia">
  <data key="d0">Latvia</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Latvia is a Baltic State where Russia is allegedly spreading propaganda about the persecution of Russian-speaking populations to justify potential military action.&lt;SEP&gt;Latvia is a country that refused to allow Robert Fico's plane to fly over its territory en route to Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Latvia is a Baltic country that denied Robert Fico permission to fly through its territory to reach Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Latvia is a Baltic nation that refused to allow Robert Fico’s aircraft to transit its airspace, signaling opposition to his pro-Kremlin overtures.</data>
