  <data key="d0">Suwałki Corridor</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Suwałki Corridor is a geographic link between Poland and Lithuania that Russia may seek to sever to isolate the Baltic States from the rest of Europe.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1a126839f1ff6597735159d84aa24a61</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Балтийские страны\6.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777932845</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hybrid Warfare">
  <data key="d0">Hybrid Warfare</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Hybrid warfare is a strategic approach involving drones, migrant flows, information campaigns, and proxy forces to destabilize and prepare for conventional military action by Russia against the Baltic States.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1a126839f1ff6597735159d84aa24a61</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Балтийские страны\6.txt</data>
