</node>
<node id="Limited Invasion">
  <data key="d0">Limited Invasion</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Limited invasion is a scenario identified by Harvard analysts as the most probable Russian military action against the Baltic States, involving rapid occupation of key infrastructure and denial of NATO response.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1a126839f1ff6597735159d84aa24a61</data>
