<node id="Литва">
  <data key="d0">Литва</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Литва is a country from which drones are alleged to launch, and has been officially declared a participant in the conflict by the speaker.&lt;SEP&gt;Литва is a country with a historical memory of Soviet occupation and repression, which shapes its strong support for Ukraine and its assessment of Russia as an existential threat.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1a2d5e0f3941015b9813c436f7443def&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1a89cef022ba72f7cec7e5ae7c29101</data>
