<node id="НАТО">
  <data key="d0">НАТО</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">НАТО is a military alliance referenced as a counterpart in the conflict, with member states including Литва and others criticized for weakness.&lt;SEP&gt;НАТО is a military alliance whose defense concepts are being reconsidered by Lithuania in response to perceived Russian threats, particularly regarding air and missile defense integration.&lt;SEP&gt;НАТО (NATO) is an international military alliance whose intelligence services are aware of Moscow's secret mission in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1a2d5e0f3941015b9813c436f7443def&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1a89cef022ba72f7cec7e5ae7c29101&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd</data>
