  <data key="d0">Европа</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Европа is described as weak, lacking subjectivity, and controlled by German interests.&lt;SEP&gt;Европа is a geographic region referenced as the context where certain representatives are acting against unity. relation Путин Европа influence, political interference Путин is described as having identified representatives within Европа who are working against European unity. relation Зеленский POLITICO statement, media communication Зеленский made a statement to POLITICO regarding Путин's actions and European unity.</data>
