  <data key="d2">The Kyiv Independent is a media outlet that published an article featuring the views of a Lithuanian individual on Russia and Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;The Kyiv Independent is a media outlet that published a report on North Korean military involvement in the war in Ukraine, authored by ЮлияТарадюк.</data>
