  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Giorgia Meloni is the Prime Minister of Italy and a right-wing conservative political leader aligned with Viktor Orbán and Fidesz in the European Parliament and EU.&lt;SEP&gt;Giorgia Meloni is the Prime Minister of Italy who opposed the transfer of frozen Russian assets to Ukraine alongside Bart de Wever, Bulgaria, and Malta.</data>
