<node id="Peter Pellegrini">
  <data key="d0">Peter Pellegrini</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Peter Pellegrini is the President of Slovakia, currently facing a political decision in March regarding a potential referendum on Robert Fico’s government. He is associated with the Epstein files due to his tenure as Prime Minister in 2019 and has denied attending Epstein’s parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-11b9d96fc698fa7b9242168a7bad3295</data>
