  <data key="d2">Slovak National Party is not explicitly mentioned in the text; however, no other political party is named as part of Fico’s coalition. Based on context, this entity is not extractable from the provided text.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovak National Party is not mentioned in the text; no entity extracted.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovak National Party is not mentioned in the text; however, the text references SMER-SD, which is a pro-Russian party led by Robert Fico.</data>
