<node id="Democrats">
  <data key="d0">Democrats</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Democrats is an extra-parliamentary political party in Slovakia, led by former Defense Minister Nagy, which collected over 350,000 signatures to initiate a referendum on removing Robert Fico’s government, revoking his pension, and restoring special investigative agencies.&lt;SEP&gt;Democrats is a pro-Western political party in Slovakia, part of the opposition coalition with approximately 47% combined support.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-11b9d96fc698fa7b9242168a7bad3295&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d2e8519cd0bab60a3e52b70a90d3f0b</data>
