<node id="Nagy">
  <data key="d0">Nagy</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Nagy is the former Minister of Defense of Slovakia and leader of the Democrats party. He was targeted by Robert Fico with criminal charges related to the transfer of aircraft to Ukraine.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-11b9d96fc698fa7b9242168a7bad3295</data>
