  <data key="d0">Juraj Šeliga</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Juraj Šeliga is the Vice President of the Democrats party in Slovakia, who expressed confidence that President Peter Pellegrini will uphold the Constitution and cooperate with the referendum initiative.</data>
