  <data key="d0">Lajčák</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Lajčák is a former Minister of Foreign Affairs in Robert Fico’s government and former advisor to the Prime Minister, mentioned over 100 times in the Epstein files, leading to his resignation amid scandal.</data>
