  <data key="d0">Epstein Files</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Epstein Files are a collection of documents related to Jeffrey Epstein, which have become central to Slovak political discourse due to multiple mentions of Lajčák and a reference to Robert Fico as a guest at a 2019 event.</data>
