  <data key="d0">Constitutional Court of the Slovak Republic</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Constitutional Court of the Slovak Republic is the judicial body to which President Peter Pellegrini may refer the referendum request, potentially delaying or blocking its implementation.</data>
