  <data key="d0">Special Prosecutors Office</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Special Prosecutor’s Office is a Slovak state institution that was abolished and is now being demanded for restoration by the Democrats party through the referendum initiative.</data>
