<node id="Hlas">
  <data key="d0">Hlas</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Hlas is a political party in Slovakia founded by Peter Pellegrini, mentioned in the context of his personal popularity being significantly higher than the party’s electoral support. relation Peter Pellegrini Hlas political affiliation, party leadership Peter Pellegrini is the founder and leader of the Hlas party, which has lower popularity compared to his personal approval ratings, highlighting a disconnect between his public image and his party’s electoral strength.&lt;SEP&gt;Hlas is a Slovak political party created as a Kremlin-backed spoiler project to split votes and enable SMER to win the 2023 Slovak elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Hlas is a political party in Slovakia whose support is approaching the 5% electoral threshold and has expressed preliminary support for Robert Fico’s electoral reform bill up to the second reading.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-11b9d96fc698fa7b9242168a7bad3295&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09de750ab096b64385f95a95c7d0e5ad</data>
