<node id="Petr Pellegrini">
  <data key="d0">Petr Pellegrini</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Petr Pellegrini is a Slovak politician who served as Prime Minister of Slovakia when the order for 14 F-16 Block 70/72 fighters was placed in 2018 and is currently the President of Slovakia.&lt;SEP&gt;Petr Pellegrini is the president of Slovakia and was initially associated with the Kremlin-backed project party Hlas, created to split votes and aid SMER's electoral success.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d0db27d1e5bd672959a82744488e5a07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495</data>
