<node id="MiG-29">
  <data key="d0">MiG-29</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">MiG-29 is a Soviet-era fighter jet originally operated by Slovakia, 13 of which were transferred to Ukraine in 2023, with four used for spare parts.</data>
