<node id="F-16 Block 70/72">
  <data key="d0">F-16 Block 70/72</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">F-16 Block 70/72 is a modernized variant of the F-16 fighter jet ordered by Slovakia in 2018 to replace its MiG-29 fleet; 10 have been delivered and four are pending.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d0db27d1e5bd672959a82744488e5a07</data>
