<node id="Czechia">
  <data key="d0">Czechia</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Czechia is a country whose fighter jets currently assist in defending Slovak airspace after the transfer of MiG-29s to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Czechia is a country where fuel prices are lower due to lack of dependence on Russian oil.&lt;SEP&gt;Czechia is a neighboring country of Hungary where retail gasoline and diesel prices are lower than in Hungary, serving as a benchmark for the inflated pricing in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d0db27d1e5bd672959a82744488e5a07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69564d3bce60628ec150d14cc9a006c7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5794dba07f2f01a805d966aa0ee2115</data>
