<node id="Пётр Мадяр">
  <data key="d0">Пётр Мадяр</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Пётр Мадяр is the head of the Hungarian opposition party "Tisa" who alleged a blackmail attempt using secretly recorded intimate video footage, claiming it was a Russian-style "honey trap" aimed at undermining his reputation ahead of crucial April elections. He accused special services of recording the footage in 2024 and possibly falsifying it, and called for the full, unedited video to be published. He is a 45-year-old man with adult sexual relationships and three minor children.</data>
