<node id="Путин">
  <data key="d0">Путин</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Путин is mentioned as a subject of criticism, which the text labels as primitive and unserious.&lt;SEP&gt;Путин is a person who, according to Зеленский, found certain representatives in Europe who began to oppose European unity.&lt;SEP&gt;Путин is the President of Russia and a strategic ally of North Korea, to whom North Korea is fulfilling military obligations by deploying troops to support operations in Ukraine.</data>
