<node id="Восток">
  <data key="d0">Восток</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Восток is mentioned as a place that those who love freedom should not fear, according to the text. relation Свинктор Торбан Восток fear,contrast Свинктор Торбан argues that those who love freedom should not fear Восток, contrasting it with the perceived threat of Брюссель.</data>
