<node id="Croatian pipeline">
  <data key="d0">Croatian pipeline</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Croatian pipeline is a transportation infrastructure that was initially deemed unsuitable but was later promoted as a viable alternative after the Druzhba pipeline was damaged.</data>
