<node id="Friendship Pipeline">
  <data key="d0">Friendship Pipeline</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Friendship Pipeline is a pipeline that was damaged by Russian shelling on January 27 and whose repair Ukraine allegedly refused, prompting Hungary to halt diesel fuel supplies.&lt;SEP&gt;The Friendship Pipeline is a pipeline that transports oil to Hungary and Slovakia and whose restoration of transit is a condition set by Hungary for allowing EU decisions on Ukraine.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b80d70d8670ebee7e64e3613a75c65de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c252425b51c0e430a65f3fb6d91f843</data>
