<node id="Bart de Wever">
  <data key="d0">Bart de Wever</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Bart de Wever is the Prime Minister of Belgium who initially opposed the transfer of frozen Russian assets to Ukraine due to Euroclear’s location in Brussels.</data>
