<node id="Bulgaria">
  <data key="d0">Bulgaria</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Bulgaria is a country that joined Giorgia Meloni and Bart de Wever in opposing the transfer of frozen Russian assets to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Bulgaria is a country where fuel prices are lower due to lack of dependence on Russian oil.</data>
