<node id="Fico">
  <data key="d0">Fico</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Fico is a political figure whose veto, alongside Babish’s, would have been overridden by a qualified majority in the European Union regarding frozen Russian assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Fico is the leader of Slovakia who supported a fact-finding mission to Ukraine and denied technical grounds for halting fuel transit despite evidence of Russian strikes.</data>
