<node id="Орбан">
  <data key="d0">Орбан</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Орбан is a political figure and the Prime Minister of Hungary who came to power following the 1998 elections and is referenced in some sources as an alternate spelling or phonetic variant of Арбанк, referring to the same individual. He is associated with a crackdown on criminal elements, including associates of Шандор Пинтер, and is linked to illicit activities disclosed by Борош Томаш. His administration has been accused of actions that may lead to formal allegations from the European Union, particularly regarding the preservation of power and potential local-level corruption. The European Union is a key context for political pressure against him, while his statements and those of his team have been targeted by the Ukrainian Ministry of Foreign Affairs’ radio program. Орбан’s party submitted a legislative proposal concerning the seizure of funds and assets from Oshchadbank, and his political stance has drawn commentary from international figures such as Kaja Kallas regarding Ukraine’s war efforts. His work is noted by Фицо as potentially continuing if he leaves office. Орбан’s main electoral opponent is Мадьяр. Additionally, Resurgam is associated with him through an invitation to engagement (“Присоединяйся”), suggesting a broader network of political or ideological alignment. A location in Budapest, Орвоньки, is mentioned as the site of an explosion near a McDonald’s, though no direct causal link to Орбан is established. Despite some conflicting references, all descriptions consistently point to a single individual: the Hungarian Prime Minister whose tenure since 1998 has been marked by controversial domestic policies and international scrutiny.&lt;SEP&gt;Орбан is a political figure who received political support from the White House administration.&lt;SEP&gt;Орбан is a political figure who faced less favorable results in the elections described in the source text.&lt;SEP&gt;Орбан is a person whose role the individual described is unwilling or unable to assume, according to the input text. relation Орбан Kremlin desire, expectation The Kremlin desires or demands that the individual assume the role of Орбан, indicating a strategic expectation from the Kremlin toward Орбан’s modeled behavior.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d20625ed121acb0490a6050249cc3df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-769ff8feb3b00c3c503fb9e86e9bdf0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50665b15c345276e9e99592c4bd0f533&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cef394908f978f54c9d7b18dd4c332a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6c1ff94c68f665c5723f439c2285eae&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b27aeca6858b7e54f862c47192fbcea2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17e8350a36758c6e44f8b72ee0cd6731&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f70e0895097bbb48ff32f2b973c6e11&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc256134299991e842abaa10ccf2b6c6</data>
