<node id="Szijjártó">
  <data key="d0">Szijjártó</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary who made the statement that Hungary will block the 20th package of sanctions unless oil transit via the Friendship pipeline is restored for Hungary and Slovakia. relation Szijjártó European Union diplomatic statement,foreign policy Szijjártó, as Hungary’s Minister of Foreign Affairs, issued a diplomatic statement directly addressing the European Union’s planned sanctions package.&lt;SEP&gt;Szijjártó is a Hungarian official who held multiple conversations with Russian Foreign Minister Lavrov regarding assistance in lifting sanctions on Russian oligarchs and coordinating actions on Ukraine.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0c252425b51c0e430a65f3fb6d91f843&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a810084503e65cb067ff1fc3c7a05189</data>
