</node>
<node id="Red Army">
  <data key="d0">Red Army</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">The Red Army is the military force that invaded Budapest in the 20th century, as referenced by Sikorski to draw a historical parallel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c1d38d0ea892917e129f8c929d603be9</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\28.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777933302</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="ruling party">
  <data key="d0">ruling party</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The ruling party in Hungary is described as using state propaganda and private media to create hostility toward Ukraine and leverage it for electoral gain.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c1d38d0ea892917e129f8c929d603be9</data>
