</node>
<node id="Russian">
  <data key="d0">Russian</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Russian is used as an adjective to describe oil, referring to oil originating from Russia. relation Russian oil origin, composition The term "Russian oil" refers to oil originating from Russia, which Hungary is implied to depend on.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-69564d3bce60628ec150d14cc9a006c7</data>
