</node>
<node id="GSCS">
  <data key="d0">GSCS</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">GSCS (State Emergency Service of Ukraine) reported a fire at an infrastructure object in Brody and advised residents to close windows and avoid going outside due to air pollution. relation GSCS Brody Pumping Station reporting,emergency response GSCS reported the fire at the Brody Pumping Station infrastructure and issued public safety advisories due to air contamination from the attack. relation Russia Druzhba disruption,attack Russia’s strike on the Brody Pumping Station disrupted the Druzhba pipeline’s oil transit, which Hungary and Slovakia falsely claimed had no technical cause.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-141360bcc1e8268affe7476ca1b210ea</data>
