<node id="Словакия">
  <data key="d0">Словакия</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Словакия is a country whose power transmission system terminated a contract for emergency electricity supply with Укрэнерго.&lt;SEP&gt;Словакия is the country of citizenship for Йозеф Рогоч.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b2842b9c04cc247c5969a9739ff25b33&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
