<node id="Martin Magát">
  <data key="d0">Martin Magát</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Martin Magát is the general director of the Slovak power transmission system who explained that the government decided to terminate the emergency power supply contract with Укрэнерго. relation Martin Magát Словакия leadership,representation Martin Magát, as general director, represents the Slovak power transmission system that terminated the contract with Укрэнерго. relation Martin Magát Укрэнерго contract termination,communication Martin Magát publicly stated the decision by the Slovak government to terminate the emergency power supply contract with Укрэнерго.</data>
