<node id="Oschadbank Ukraine">
  <data key="d0">Oschadbank Ukraine</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Oschadbank Ukraine is the Ukrainian branch of Oschadbank that conducted the international transport of foreign currency and banking metals with Raiffeisen Bank Austria. relation Oschadbank Ukraine Raiffeisen Bank Austria international agreement,financial transport Oschadbank Ukraine transported foreign currency and banking metals to Raiffeisen Bank Austria under an international agreement. relation Oschadbank Ukraine Hungary detention,unlawful seizure Oschadbank Ukraine’s armored vehicles and employees were unlawfully detained by authorities in Hungary during a routine transport. relation Oschadbank Oschadbank Ukraine organizational affiliation Oschadbank Ukraine is the Ukrainian operational entity of Oschadbank, which is referenced in the text as the entity involved in the transport.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-04a007153cdf32c13e7e322795fc37d0</data>
