  <data key="d5">1777933722</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sergei Kirienko">
  <data key="d0">Sergei Kirienko</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sergei Kirienko is the First Deputy Chief of the Russian Presidential Administration and the architect of Russia's domestic and foreign political influence infrastructure, tasked by the Russian government with managing operations in Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergei Kirienko is a senior Russian official and former Prime Minister of Russia, currently overseeing Russian foreign influence operations, including those in Hungary and Moldova.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1284d93bbeeeb191a35ec243b4ce4b07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95251bcfc4d08a0a36c341b9a9e2da54</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\40.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936513</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Russian Military Intelligence">
  <data key="d0">Russian Military Intelligence</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">Russian Military Intelligence is the intelligence branch of the Russian armed forces that, under Putin's orders, participated in interfering in Hungary's parliamentary elections. relation Russian Military Intelligence Hungary interference, election manipulation Russian Military Intelligence, directed by Putin and managed by Sergei Kirienko, participated in efforts to interfere in Hungary's parliamentary elections to ensure Viktor Orbán's victory.&lt;SEP&gt;Russian Military Intelligence is a Russian intelligence agency whose operatives are reported to have arrived in Hungary, corroborating prior investigations into Russian interference in Hungarian elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Russian Military Intelligence is the Russian military intelligence agency whose operatives were reported to have entered Hungary to support Russian influence operations, as confirmed by European security officials.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1284d93bbeeeb191a35ec243b4ce4b07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-583ccb318ed3bd5eb71b569940315d4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-325a7fb30b39d268db124a71f1e8acc7</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\40.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\95.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\96.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777934203</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ощадбанк">
  <data key="d0">Ощадбанк</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Ощадбанк is a bank whose cash-in-transit employees were detained, and the money they were transporting may belong to a mafia.&lt;SEP&gt;Ощадбанк is a Ukrainian financial institution whose funds and assets are the subject of a legislative proposal in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d33a21fd3bcedf316781cb497ea0a2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-769ff8feb3b00c3c503fb9e86e9bdf0b</data>
