</node>
<node id="National Tax and Customs Administration">
  <data key="d0">National Tax and Customs Administration</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">National Tax and Customs Administration is the Hungarian authority that identified the identities of seven Ukrainian citizens detained for importing money and gold into Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-350a5144d8e2787035e85988d9818a16</data>
