</node>
<node id="Security Service of Ukraine">
  <data key="d0">Security Service of Ukraine</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Security Service of Ukraine is the former employer of the general who led the group of deported cash-in-transit officers.&lt;SEP&gt;The Security Service of Ukraine is an organization that identified a Hungarian intelligence officer and dismantled an espionage network operating in Zakarpattia, arresting two members and investigating the network's activities since spring 2025.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-350a5144d8e2787035e85988d9818a16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d66247a37e4df218b0d4f4b7d7bea3c4</data>
