</node>
<node id="Ukrainian Air Force">
  <data key="d0">Ukrainian Air Force</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">Ukrainian Air Force is the former employer of the deputy leader of the group of deported cash-in-transit officers, who was a former major.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-350a5144d8e2787035e85988d9818a16</data>
