<node id="Seven Ukrainian Cash-in-Transit Officers">
  <data key="d0">Seven Ukrainian Cash-in-Transit Officers</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Seven Ukrainian Cash-in-Transit Officers are individuals employed by Oshchadbank who were detained and deported from Hungary for importing money and gold, led by a former SBU general and assisted by personnel with military experience.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-350a5144d8e2787035e85988d9818a16</data>
