</node>
<node id="April 12">
  <data key="d0">April 12</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">April 12 is the date of the upcoming Hungarian elections, which Peter Magyar urges citizens to participate in to reject foreign interference.&lt;SEP&gt;April 12 is the date of the Hungarian parliamentary elections, which served as the deadline for Orbán’s political strategy to demonstrate victory over Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;April 12 is the date of the Hungarian elections, which Viktor Orban frames as a choice between his leadership and a puppet president installed by Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;April 12 is the date of the upcoming elections in Hungary. entity April 7–8 event April 7–8 is the scheduled dates for the visit of the U.S. vice president to Hungary in support of Orbán. relation Orbán April 12 election participation, political timeline Orbán is the incumbent prime minister participating in the Hungarian elections scheduled for April 12. relation Vance April 7–8 diplomatic visit, scheduled event Vance, vice president of the United States, is scheduled to visit Hungary on April 7–8 to support Orbán.&lt;SEP&gt;April 12 is a date referenced as the timing of upcoming Hungarian elections, which influenced the European Union’s delayed and muted response to the Siyarta scandal.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b2025a50f1328b82f061a4942a8dd453&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-febe32c9e0da364a16a64ecb34a3ae7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c8eeb9a8a3df6bc82ea6fb1da68ab0e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81536517f133c3a5924be660cac3eb05&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\50.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\53.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\81.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\126.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936516</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Операция «Будапешт»">
  <data key="d0">Операция «Будапешт»</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Операция «Будапешт» is a covert Russian operation aimed at preserving Viktor Orbán in power ahead of Hungary's parliamentary elections, involving a special team sent to Budapest and curated by Sergei Kirienko.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\51.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777933722</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Калитин Андрей Сергеевич">
  <data key="d0">Калитин Андрей Сергеевич</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Калитин Андрей Сергеевич is identified as a foreign agent responsible for producing, distributing, or directing the material described in the source text.</data>
