  <data key="d0">Москва</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Москва is the capital of Russia and the origin of a covert operation targeting Hungary's political landscape ahead of parliamentary elections.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd</data>
