<node id="Будапешт">
  <data key="d0">Будапешт</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Будапешт is the capital of Hungary and the destination of a secret Russian mission aimed at influencing the outcome of parliamentary elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Будапешт is the location where the march in support of Мадьяр took place.&lt;SEP&gt;Будапешт is the capital city of Hungary, from which the speaker was to be transported to Сомбатхей after sentencing.&lt;SEP&gt;Будапешт is the city in Hungary where the meeting with Игорь’s associate occurred and where the assassination attempt took place.&lt;SEP&gt;Будапешт is the capital city of Hungary, serving as the base of operations for the individuals who visited the speaker in prison.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cef394908f978f54c9d7b18dd4c332a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85ab176e3cbddf97c2d5cd15191ff861</data>
