  <data key="d0">Сергей Кириенко</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Сергей Кириенко is the chief architect of Russia's political influence infrastructure, both domestically and internationally, and is in charge of curating the operation in Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd</data>
