  <data key="d0">Майя Санду</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Майя Санду is the pro-Western president of Moldova who was the target of Russian influence operations orchestrated by Sergei Kirienko's network.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd</data>
