  <data key="d0">Вадим Титов</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Вадим Титов is a political administrator and former official from Rosatom who now leads the newly established Unit for Strategic Partnership and Cooperation, tasked with managing Russian influence operations in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd</data>
