  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Фидес is the ruling political party of Hungary, represented by Máté Kócsi, which submitted a legislative proposal concerning Oshchadbank's assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Фидес is a political organization that experienced less favorable outcomes in the elections described in the source text.</data>
