  <data key="d0">Фицо</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Фицо is a person who hinted that someone might continue the work of Orbán if Orbán is no longer in power. entity Орбан person Орбан is a person whose work was referenced by Фицо as potentially being continued by someone else if Орбан is no longer in power. relation Фицо Орбан continuation of work,political succession Фицо hinted that someone might continue the work of Орбан if Орбан is no longer in power, implying a potential political succession or alignment in policy.</data>
