</node>
<node id="Social Design Agency">
  <data key="d0">Social Design Agency</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Social Design Agency is an agency linked to the Kremlin that developed a disinformation campaign in favor of Viktor Orbán for the upcoming elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Social Design Agency is a Russian organization designated by the United States in 2024 for conducting disinformation operations, including creating fake Western news sites, and is now coordinating disinformation campaigns in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3960e17c128f750dfd948945c91a00ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3da3b046ca1fff9119eaf735e34f56d4</data>
