<node id="Spoiler Technique">
  <data key="d0">Spoiler Technique</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The spoiler technique is an electoral strategy involving a candidate with identical name and initials to a major opponent, designed to divert votes through voter confusion, particularly among older voters, and is characteristic of post-Soviet electoral environments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3311af1794addd390d80bf21ccd47d8f</data>
