<node id="Volodymyr Zelenskyy">
  <data key="d0">Volodymyr Zelenskyy</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Volodymyr Zelenskyy is the President of Ukraine who is accused by Viktor Orbán of maintaining an oil pipeline blockade despite its critical impact on Hungary and Slovakia.&lt;SEP&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy is the President of Ukraine, who is allegedly associated with an influential Ukrainian figure accused by Hungarian media of threatening Viktor Orbán.&lt;SEP&gt;Volodymyr Zelenskyy is the president of Ukraine who believes that negotiations with Vladimir Putin will eventually be necessary under the right conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f3dc55aad4eb94544269bbfd9dec2905&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c4fcaac079096c59954da324c3f17538&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3117b3a03ff471f00f67b26aade3e091</data>
