<node id="Facebook">
  <data key="d0">Facebook</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Facebook is the platform where Viktor Orbán published his pre-election video containing statements about Ukraine, Russian oil, and European sanctions. relation Viktor Orbán Facebook publication,communication Viktor Orbán used Facebook to publish a pre-election video in which he made statements about Ukraine’s oil blockade and European energy policy.&lt;SEP&gt;Facebook is a platform where 44 thousand people watched Madyar's speech and 9–10 thousand people watched Viktor Orban's speech. entity YouTube organization YouTube is a platform where 87 thousand people watched Madyar's speech and 4 thousand people watched Viktor Orban's speech. relation Madyar Facebook audience, viewership Madyar's speech was watched by 44 thousand people on Facebook. relation Madyar YouTube audience, viewership Madyar's speech was watched by 87 thousand people on YouTube. relation Viktor Orban Facebook audience, viewership Viktor Orban's speech was watched by 9–10 thousand people on Facebook. relation Viktor Orban YouTube audience, viewership Viktor Orban's speech was watched by 4 thousand people on YouTube.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f3dc55aad4eb94544269bbfd9dec2905&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2c604c4b50688beffa97c1aa0f1b779</data>
