  <data key="d0">DW Украина</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">DW Украина is an organization that is being encouraged for subscription in the input text, associated with video content about Ukraine. relation Орбана DW Украина media reference,content sharing The input text directs viewers to watch video content from DW Украина regarding Орбана’s remarks, implying a media linkage between the two.</data>
