<node id="Uzhhorod">
  <data key="d0">Uzhhorod</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Uzhhorod is a city referenced in separatist banners in Hungary, falsely asserted to be a Hungarian city.&lt;SEP&gt;Uzhhorod is a city in Ukraine near the borders of Slovakia and Hungary, where the translator grew up and was exposed to multilingual and cross-border environments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f3eae0bc40cda4dae9e8683de1c3851c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725</data>
