<node id="January 27">
  <data key="d0">January 27</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">January 27 is the date of a Russian strike that damaged the Ukrainian section of the "Druzhba" pipeline. relation European Union Druzhba financial support, technical assistance The European Union will finance the repair of the "Druzhba" pipeline and provide technical support following damage from the January 27 strike. relation Viktor Orbán Robert Fico funding blockade coordination Viktor Orbán and Robert Fico are both expected to maintain the blockade of €90 billion for Ukraine, indicating coordinated political resistance to unlocking funds.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0b9d4541f93fbe1abbecc6f52128db7e</data>
