  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="West">
  <data key="d0">West</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The West refers to Western countries that pursued Ukraine’s integration into NATO and the European Union, which Orbán claims provoked Russia’s response.&lt;SEP&gt;The West refers to Western nations and institutions that initially supported Orbán as a liberal icon but later became his political adversaries.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f2ed677b91cd8a20441c02fa69439eac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ccbba289defe85bee861c66ae67de11</data>
