<node id="Soviet Foreign Intelligence Service">
  <data key="d0">Soviet Foreign Intelligence Service</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Soviet Foreign Intelligence Service (SVR) is a Russian intelligence organization that developed a covert strategy codenamed "Gamechanger" to influence the Hungarian parliamentary elections by simulating an assassination attempt on Viktor Orbán.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-583ccb318ed3bd5eb71b569940315d4f</data>
