</node>
<node id="Tigran Garibyan">
  <data key="d0">Tigran Garibyan</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Tigran Garibyan is a Russian diplomatic envoy and advisor at the Russian embassy in Budapest who regularly meets with pro-government Hungarian journalists to disseminate Russian disinformation narratives.&lt;SEP&gt;Tigran Garibyan is a Russian diplomatic advisor at the Russian Embassy in Budapest who coordinates pro-government Hungarian media campaigns by providing instructions to journalists aligned with Viktor Orbán.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-583ccb318ed3bd5eb71b569940315d4f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-325a7fb30b39d268db124a71f1e8acc7</data>
