</node>
<node id="Peter Szijjártó">
  <data key="d0">Peter Szijjártó</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Peter Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary who regularly communicates with Russian Foreign Minister Sergey Lavrov during EU meetings, providing real-time intelligence on EU discussions.&lt;SEP&gt;Peter Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary who signed the 12-point cooperation agreement with Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Peter Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary who maintained a direct communication line with Russian Foreign Minister Sergey Lavrov, disclosing confidential EU discussions during wartime.&lt;SEP&gt;Peter Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary who allegedly destroyed documents related to sanctions.&lt;SEP&gt;Peter Szijjártó is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary who allegedly passed information about closed European Union meetings to Russian entities, leading to accusations of treason by the opposition.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-325a7fb30b39d268db124a71f1e8acc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1d17587159dea209c75a0ae5875a4b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4089c9c991c6402b317d88ca6848ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b58528cbdfa8a329180c462cc03756dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1c1527de328b9a19ce7197568a1196b</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\96.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\135.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\186.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\109.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1778011252</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
  <data key="d7">Peter Szijjártó</data>
</node>
<node id="Sergey Lavrov">
  <data key="d0">Sergey Lavrov</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sergey Lavrov is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Russia who receives direct, real-time briefings from Hungarian Foreign Minister Peter Szijjártó during EU sessions.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is the Russian Minister of Foreign Affairs who received confidential reports from the Hungarian Foreign Minister regarding EU discussions and Slovak elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is a Russian official who was proposed to receive European Union documents via the Hungarian embassy in Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is the Russian Foreign Minister who engaged in a conversation with the Hungarian Foreign Minister regarding Ukraine's EU accession and requested documents related to minority rights formulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Russia who had direct, confidential communications with Hungary’s Foreign Minister Peter Szijjártó regarding EU decision-making processes.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov is the Russian Foreign Minister who has been directly involved in discussions with Hungarian officials regarding sanctions, as revealed by intercepted communications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-325a7fb30b39d268db124a71f1e8acc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9360bf859acb934b8ebad024d1c18290&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c69b4fdab693c5bb396f844f3d8a77c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4089c9c991c6402b317d88ca6848ab9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de92df91fd68b8019a5e2c98e87d545e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\96.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\101.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\136.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\138.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936512</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ferenc Fres">
  <data key="d0">Ferenc Fres</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Ferenc Fres is the former head of Hungary’s cyber defense service who disclosed that Russian hackers infiltrated Hungarian government networks to provide Moscow with access to sensitive EU discussions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-325a7fb30b39d268db124a71f1e8acc7</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\96.txt</data>
