  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Lavrov">
  <data key="d0">Lavrov</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sergei Lavrov is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Russia, a position in which he has engaged in multiple high-level diplomatic interactions with foreign officials, particularly during closed European Union meetings. He has communicated regularly with Hungarian Minister of Foreign Affairs Péter Szijjártó, discussing coordinated actions regarding Ukraine’s potential EU accession, including instructions to block negotiations and seeking to obtain documents related to minority rights language. Lavrov has also directly contacted Szijjártó on behalf of Russian oligarch Alisher Usmanov, requesting the removal of Usmanov’s sister from EU sanctions lists and relaying broader appeals from Usmanov. In these exchanges, Lavrov expressed approval of Szijjártó’s statements and criticized EU leadership. Additionally, Lavrov has been referenced in the context of leaked phone conversations with Slovak officials, which may have implicated political figures such as Robert Fico. These interactions, as reported by various sources, indicate Lavrov’s active role in advancing Russian geopolitical and oligarchic interests through diplomatic channels within the EU framework.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba1043e375054a4f318c66342ee9ad31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-efac8eca24c7251212c13175865647fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6610955fc2b94d091c65e9f7449d2028&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4398c1136d9d0745f3589421281ecc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d35dd378774e42749ede8cf940deb5eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a810084503e65cb067ff1fc3c7a05189&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9bcca043358a8f1b8a9a2999a79a6f6</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\97.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\100.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\118.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\119.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\137.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\184.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\198.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777938039</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Washington Post">
  <data key="d0">Washington Post</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Washington Post is a news organization that reported on Siyarto's communications with Lavrov.&lt;SEP&gt;Washington Post is a news organization that published a report based on an intercepted and independently verified Russian SVR document detailing a plan to stage a fake assassination attempt on Viktor Orbán.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ba1043e375054a4f318c66342ee9ad31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3da3b046ca1fff9119eaf735e34f56d4</data>
