</node>
<node id="Hungarian Military Intelligence">
  <data key="d0">Hungarian Military Intelligence</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Hungarian Military Intelligence is the organization that employed Zoltan Andre as a staff member and directed his espionage and sabotage operations against Ukraine, including the use of diplomatic cover and recruitment through incentives.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d66247a37e4df218b0d4f4b7d7bea3c4</data>
