</node>
<node id="SMER">
  <data key="d0">SMER</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Smer is a political party led by Robert Fico with concentrated regional support, facing declining popularity and targeted by electoral reforms to reduce opposition influence.&lt;SEP&gt;SMER is a Slovak social-democratic political party that was targeted for electoral support by Hungarian and Russian actors; Robert Fico previously led it and returned in 2023.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09de750ab096b64385f95a95c7d0e5ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495</data>
