</node>
<node id="Romania">
  <data key="d0">Romania</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Romania is a country referenced as an example of the European Union taking action against a member state through intelligence leaks, similar to the case involving Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Romania is a country where Russian influence operations, similar to those conducted in Hungary, were previously carried out using coordinated disinformation tactics.&lt;SEP&gt;Romania is a country that served as a transit route for Robert Fico's flight to Moscow during the previous year's parade.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95251bcfc4d08a0a36c341b9a9e2da54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81f9a312226a282bf8ebf1aee5ad788a</data>
