</node>
<node id="Progressive Slovakia">
  <data key="d0">Progressive Slovakia</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Progressive Slovakia is a pro-Western political party in Slovakia, part of the opposition coalition with approximately 47% combined support.&lt;SEP&gt;Progressive Slovakia is an opposition party in Slovakia that is a potential ally of mid-sized parties and is negatively affected by Robert Fico’s proposed electoral changes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0d2e8519cd0bab60a3e52b70a90d3f0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09de750ab096b64385f95a95c7d0e5ad</data>
