<node id="HLAS-SD">
  <data key="d0">HLAS-SD</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">HLAS-SD is a pro-Russian ultraleft political party in Slovakia led by Pellegrini, part of the pro-Russian coalition with approximately 38% combined support.</data>
