  <data key="d2">Kirienko is a deputy head of the Russian presidential administration whose bot operations exhibit a similar pattern to those targeting Hungarian discourse in Russian Telegram channels.&lt;SEP&gt;Kirienko is a Russian official associated with coordinating Russian interference in Moldovan elections and later in Hungarian politics.</data>
