  <data key="d0">Sergei Lavrov</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sergei Lavrov is the Russian Foreign Minister who communicated with Siyarto, acknowledged his alignment with Russian interests, and relayed requests from Russian oligarch Alisher Usmanov regarding sanctions relief.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergei Lavrov is the Russian Foreign Minister with whom Hungary’s Foreign Minister is subservient.</data>
