  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alisher Usmanov is a Russian oligarch who requested assistance from Siyarto to have his sister, Ismailova, removed from the EU sanctions list.&lt;SEP&gt;Alisher Usmanov is a Russian oligarch closely associated with Putin, who has been subject to European sanctions and whose assets include the yacht Delbar.</data>
