  <data key="d0">Ismailova</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Ismailova is the sister of Alisher Usmanov, who was removed from the EU sanctions list after intervention by Siyarto and Slovak officials.&lt;SEP&gt;Ismailova is the sister of Alisher Usmanov, who was removed from the EU sanctions list in February 2025 after lobbying by Hungary and Slovakia.</data>
