  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Kantor is a Russian businessman who was removed from the EU sanctions list alongside Ismailova and Degtyarev following pressure from Hungary and Slovakia.&lt;SEP&gt;Kantor is a Russian businessman who was removed from the EU sanctions list alongside Ismailova and Degtyarev.</data>
