  <data key="d0">Degtyarev</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Degtyarev is the Russian Minister of Sport who was removed from the EU sanctions list after Hungary and Slovakia threatened to block the extension of sanctions.&lt;SEP&gt;Degtyarev is the Russian Minister of Sport who was removed from the EU sanctions list alongside Ismailova and Kantor.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bde507aa2566c6c22d3e526f2ec971df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6610955fc2b94d091c65e9f7449d2028</data>
