  <data key="d0">Sorokin</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sorokin is the Deputy Minister of Energy of Russia who received updates from Siyarto regarding efforts to undermine EU sanctions packages targeting Russian energy and financial entities.&lt;SEP&gt;Sorokin is the Deputy Minister of Energy of Russia who received reports from Siyarto regarding efforts to undermine EU sanctions against shadow fleets and Russian banks.</data>
