  <data key="d0">2Rivers</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">2Rivers is a Dubai-based company trading Russian oil that sought exemption from EU sanctions, with Siyarto complaining about lack of transparency from the EU regarding its inclusion.&lt;SEP&gt;2Rivers is a Dubai-based company that trades Russian oil and is subject to proposed sanctions by the European Union.&lt;SEP&gt;2Rivers is a Dubai-based company involved in trading Russian oil that was targeted by proposed EU sanctions, which Siyarto sought to prevent.</data>
