  <data key="d0">Gazprom</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Gazprom is the Russian state-owned energy company whose headquarters Siyarto visited, and which remains central to Hungary’s energy dependence on Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Gazprom is the Russian state-owned energy company whose headquarters Siyarto visited, indicating close ties with Russian energy institutions.</data>
