<node id="The Insider">
  <data key="d0">The Insider</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Insider is an investigative media organization that obtained and published recorded conversations between Siyarto and Russian officials, revealing covert coordination on sanctions evasion.&lt;SEP&gt;The Insider is an investigative media organization that obtained and published recordings of communications between Siyarto and Russian officials.&lt;SEP&gt;The Insider is an organization that produces investigative content, including an interview about corruption and organized crime in Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;The Insider is a media organization that co-published an investigative report containing the transcript of the conversation between Sergey Lavrov and Péter Szijjártó.</data>
