<node id="Dmytro Korniienko">
  <data key="d0">Dmytro Korniienko</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Dmytro Korniienko is a Ukrainian political scientist and founder of Resurgam, accused by Hungarian propaganda of threatening Viktor Orbán with a sword, though he denies any such threats and claims the claims are fabricated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c4fcaac079096c59954da324c3f17538</data>
