</node>
<node id="RT Balkan">
  <data key="d0">RT Balkan</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">RT Balkan is a Russian-backed media outlet used to disseminate the false narrative about Dmytro Korniienko and Viktor Orbán, according to the source text.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c4fcaac079096c59954da324c3f17538</data>
