<node id="18th Sanctions Package">
  <data key="d0">18th Sanctions Package</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The 18th sanctions package is a set of EU sanctions targeting Russian banks and energy entities, which Siyarto worked to weaken by requesting exclusions and delaying implementation.&lt;SEP&gt;The 18th Sanctions Package is a European Union document targeting Russian companies and banks, which Siyarto has worked to weaken by removing entities from its list.&lt;SEP&gt;The 18th Sanctions Package is a set of EU sanctions measures from which 72 out of 128 positions were allegedly removed due to lobbying by Siyarta with Russian officials.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bde507aa2566c6c22d3e526f2ec971df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b346b60f2318d240edb84608cb2b374</data>
