  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Министерство иностранных дел Украины is an organization that launched the radio program "Венгерское радио Украины" to counter Hungarian Prime Minister Orbán's disinformation and anti-Ukrainian propaganda.</data>
