  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">"Венгерское радио Украины" is a 24-hour radio program launched by the Ukrainian Ministry of Foreign Affairs to respond to false narratives and anti-Ukrainian propaganda by Orbán and his government.</data>
