<node id="Dmitriev">
  <data key="d0">Dmitriev</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Dmitriev is Putin's special representative who praised Viktor Orbán as a voice of wisdom and common sense in Europe regarding the energy and economic crisis.&lt;SEP&gt;Dmitriev is a Russian official involved in leaked conversations with Uitkoft regarding a peace plan and coordination between Moscow and Washington.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9aedd80ca30611f4314d3afe2ee2ad0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a810084503e65cb067ff1fc3c7a05189</data>
