</node>
<node id="Energy Crisis">
  <data key="d0">Energy Crisis</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The energy crisis is a severe global situation referenced as a critical threat to Europe, with calls to remove sanctions on Russian energy to mitigate its impact.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9aedd80ca30611f4314d3afe2ee2ad0</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\123.txt</data>
