</node>
<node id="Tusk">
  <data key="d0">Tusk</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Tusk is a political figure who made a statement claiming that Donald Trump's actions benefit Russia and reflect Putin's dreams. relation Tusk Donald Trump criticism,accusation Tusk stated that Donald Trump's actions benefit Russia and are aligned with Putin's dreams, prompting Viktor Orbán’s response. relation Tusk Vladimir Putin alignment,accusation Tusk accused Donald Trump of acting in alignment with Vladimir Putin’s interests, framing Trump’s policies as Putin’s dream.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d9aedd80ca30611f4314d3afe2ee2ad0</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\123.txt</data>
