</node>
<node id="1956 Hungarian Uprising">
  <data key="d0">1956 Hungarian Uprising</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The 1956 Hungarian Uprising was a nationwide revolt against Soviet control, during which the slogan "Russians home" emerged.&lt;SEP&gt;The 1956 Hungarian Uprising was a national revolt against Soviet control, remembered by Hungarians and cited as a reason for strong anti-Russian sentiment in the country.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-81536517f133c3a5924be660cac3eb05&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a810084503e65cb067ff1fc3c7a05189</data>
