  <data key="d0">Игорь Король</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Игорь Король was a criminal associate of Семён Могилевич who collected money for small-scale criminal activities and acted as an intermediary in bribe deliveries to Hungarian officials.&lt;SEP&gt;Игорь Король is a person with whom the speaker had close personal and professional interactions, and who gave orders related to violent acts and money deliveries.&lt;SEP&gt;Игорь Король is a figure in a criminal network who received a complaint from a woman who was severely injured, and who had a hierarchical relationship with Леонид Цецюра.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol is a person who was held in pre-trial detention for nine months, was not convicted, and later attacked the speaker’s childhood friend. He is described as having a wife of Hungarian nationality and a daughter born during his detention.&lt;SEP&gt;Игорь Король is a person who was involved in violent activities, attempted to appease the speaker, and was deported from Hungary after attempting to invest money in a casino in Bucharest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Леонид Цецюра">
  <data key="d0">Леонид Цецюра</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Леонид Цецюра is a person of Jewish origin who led a brigade that severely injured a woman; he was lower in hierarchy than Игорь Король and was protected by Сева.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Сева">
  <data key="d0">Сева</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Сева is a person who mediated conflicts within the criminal hierarchy, specifically protecting Леонид Цецюра from Игорь Король’s retaliation.&lt;SEP&gt;Seva is mentioned as an individual associated with an office, but no further details about identity or role are provided.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Могилевич, Семён">
  <data key="d0">Могилевич, Семён</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Могилевич, Семён is a person of Jewish origin who knew Леонид Цецюра from early youth and was part of the same criminal circle.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Пинтер, Шандер">
  <data key="d0">Пинтер, Шандер</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Пинтер, Шандер is the chief of police who received payments from Могилевич and was aligned with Виктор Арбан.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Виктор Арбан">
  <data key="d0">Виктор Арбан</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Виктор Арбан is a political figure who received financial support from Могилевич to win the 1998 elections and later became Minister of Internal Affairs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Корона">
  <data key="d0">Корона</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Корона is a hotel where Игорь Король met with the injured woman.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Камигами">
  <data key="d0">Камигами</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Камигами is a small restaurant located opposite the Корона hotel, where the injured woman met with Игорь Король.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Магилевич">
  <data key="d0">Магилевич</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Магилевич is a businessman who provided financial payments to Пинтер, Шандер and Виктор Арбан to influence political outcomes.&lt;SEP&gt;Магилевич is a person who had close ties to Шандор Пинтер, possessed compromising information on Орбан, and reportedly fled to Russia.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="1998 Elections">
  <data key="d0">1998 Elections</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The 1998 Elections were a political event in which Виктор Арбан won, leading to his appointment as Minister of Internal Affairs and improved conditions for Магилевич.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Лотци">
  <data key="d0">Лотци</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Лотци is a person who was instructed by Сева to deliver money to Виктор Арбан, as mentioned in the context of election funding. relation Сева Лотци instruction, money delivery Сева instructed Лотци to deliver money to Виктор Арбан, indicating a chain of command in the financial operations supporting the election campaign. relation Лотци Виктор Арбан money delivery, election funding Лотци delivered large sums of money to Виктор Арбан on behalf of Сева, directly supporting his 1998 election campaign.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42453f70a393d3fdaae19dd559f506ab</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Оля Игоря">
  <data key="d0">Оля Игоря</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Olya Igorya is mentioned in the context of an office location associated with Seva, but no further details about identity or role are provided.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
