</node>
<node id="Александр Киричанин">
  <data key="d0">Александр Киричанин</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alexander Kirichanin is the speaker’s childhood friend who lived in Hungary since 1994, worked as a businessman, had a family with five children, and was assaulted and robbed by Igor Korol.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936105</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Будоверш">
  <data key="d0">Будоверш</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Budoverš is a town immediately after Budapest, where Alexander Kirichanin was assaulted and where the speaker met him after receiving distress calls.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Сантендра">
  <data key="d0">Сантендра</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Szentendre is a town near Budapest, mentioned as a reference point for the location of Budoverš.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="НКУизер Джип">
  <data key="d0">НКУизер Джип</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">NkUizer Jeep is the vehicle stolen from Alexander Kirichanin during the assault by Igor Korol’s associates.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Пинтер">
  <data key="d0">Пинтер</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Пинтер is a person involved in real estate and criminal activities who ordered the assassination of Присташ Йожеф due to a business conflict.&lt;SEP&gt;Pinter is a person referenced as someone with whom a deal was made to prevent Igor Korol’s conviction.&lt;SEP&gt;Пинтер is a person referenced by the speaker as someone who would be imprisoned if Игорь continued his threats.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9eb97f8c573cf721a0206d7b0dff7868&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Игорь">
  <data key="d0">Игорь</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Игорь is a person who had a conflict with the speaker after the 1998 elections, due to aggressive actions against the speaker’s childhood friend, Саша Киричанин.&lt;SEP&gt;Игорь is a dangerous individual involved in violent actions, who was the main initiator of an attack on the speaker and later attempted to appease him after being confronted.&lt;SEP&gt;Игорь is an individual who had close personal relations with the speaker and discussed the assassination of Борош Томаш with him shortly after it occurred in 1996. relation Игорь Борош Томаш knowledge sharing,informant network Игорь discussed the assassination of Борош Томаш with the speaker, indicating awareness of the event and its context, likely through shared intelligence or personal connections. relation Пинтер Шандор Игорь association,shared knowledge Пинтер Шандор’s actions and the assassination of Борош Томаш were known to Игорь, who discussed them with the speaker, suggesting a broader network of individuals aware of the crime.&lt;SEP&gt;Игорь is a person involved in a criminal group who threatened the speaker, demanded a meeting, and was associated with a car used by the group.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Радченко Руслан">
  <data key="d0">Радченко Руслан</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Радченко Руслан was a deputy in Игорь’s group, who fell out with Игорь, later revealed to the speaker the details of the attack against him, and implicated Игорь as the main instigator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Steec Nutrition">
  <data key="d0">Steec Nutrition</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Steec Nutrition is a company based in Hungary that sponsored the speaker, enabling him to live off sales of sports supplements such as proteins, amino acids, and vitamins.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bucharest">
  <data key="d0">Bucharest</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Bucharest is a city where Игорь began moving his money, likely to evade consequences or secure assets after being confronted by the speaker.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="1999">
  <data key="d0">1999</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">1999 is the year when the speaker resumed competing in sports events approximately eleven months after the attack.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="December 23">
  <data key="d0">December 23</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">December 23 is the date when people in Budapest were preparing for Christmas, occurring around the time of the speaker’s attack.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="December 31">
  <data key="d0">December 31</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">December 31 is the date when the speaker was discharged from the hospital and celebrated New Year’s Day at home.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="2001">
  <data key="d0">2001</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">2001 is the year when Радченко Руслан reconnected with the speaker and revealed the truth about the attack orchestrated by Игорь.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Дочь">
  <data key="d0">Дочь</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Дочь is the speaker’s daughter who, along with the wife, described to the speaker how he lost consciousness, his tongue fell back, and he began choking after the attack. entity Жена person Жена is the speaker’s wife who immediately called emergency services after the attack and was involved in his medical care and recovery. relation Жена Дочь collaboration,medical_support Жена and Дочь jointly provided accounts to the speaker of the events following his collapse, including his loss of consciousness and the medical interventions performed. relation Жена Budapest emergency_response Жена called emergency services in Budapest after the speaker was attacked and experienced severe blood loss. relation Дочь Budapest witness,medical_support Дочь was present during the medical emergency in Budapest and later recounted details of the speaker’s condition to him. relation Игорь Hungary residence,operational_base Игорь operated in Hungary, where the attack on the speaker occurred and where Steec Nutrition was based, indicating his presence and influence in the country. relation Steec Nutrition Hungary location,operation Steec Nutrition is an organization that operated in Hungary and sponsored the speaker during his recovery and return to sports.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Могилевич">
  <data key="d0">Могилевич</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Могилевич is a person who delivered money in the presence of the speaker, and the money was passed to the king, who then gave it to the speaker.&lt;SEP&gt;Могилевич is a participant in illicit activities connected to Борош Томаш and Пинтер Шандор, as referenced in the testimony.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Король">
  <data key="d0">Король</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Король is a person who received money from Могилевич and subsequently delivered it to the speaker, often with instructions such as "вот лодцы потом повезёшь".</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Славик">
  <data key="d0">Славик</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Славик is a Ukrainian man who was shot through a car window, leading to a case that required closure through the delivery of money.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Эдик">
  <data key="d0">Эдик</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Эдик, also known by the nickname Дуцы, is a person from Ужгород who was shot and killed while walking to the beach in the summer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Присташ Йожеф">
  <data key="d0">Присташ Йожеф</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Присташ Йожеф is a wealthy and rigid businessman in real estate who was shot and killed after refusing to sell property to Пинтер.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Портик Томаш">
  <data key="d0">Портик Томаш</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Портик Томаш is a person who worked with Пинтер and was tasked with carrying out the assassination of Присташ Йожеф.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Йозеф Рогоч">
  <data key="d0">Йозеф Рогоч</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Йозеф Рогоч is a citizen of Slovakia who executed the assassination of Присташ Йожеф by shooting him near his jeep.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ужгород">
  <data key="d0">Ужгород</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Ужгород is a location where Эдик grew up and from which he originated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="проститутка">
  <data key="d0">проститутка</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Проститутка is a single mother of three children who was killed, and her death was covered up as part of the pattern of violent closures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="деньги">
  <data key="d0">деньги</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Деньги refer to cash payments, typically in U.S. dollars, ranging from $30,000 to $50,000 per packet, delivered to close cases related to murders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Йожеф Присташ">
  <data key="d0">Йожеф Присташ</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Йожеф Присташ is a wealthy and rigid real estate businessman who was assassinated after refusing to sell property to Пинтер. entity Пристаж person Пристаж is an alternate spelling or mispronunciation of Йожеф Присташ, referring to the same individual who was shot dead. relation Пинтер Йожеф Присташ business conflict, assassination order Пинтер ordered the assassination of Йожеф Присташ after he refused to sell real estate, leading to his murder. relation Портик Томаш Йожеф Присташ assassination assignment Портик Томаш was tasked by Пинтер to arrange the killing of Йожеф Присташ, acting as an intermediary in the execution order.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Борош Томаш">
  <data key="d0">Борош Томаш</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Борош Томаш was an individual involved in illicit activities related to diesel fuel and paint trafficking, who later provided detailed testimony to police about connections between Mogilevich, Orbán, and others, resulting in a video recording of his disclosures. He was assassinated by a car bomb in Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Пинтер Шандор">
  <data key="d0">Пинтер Шандор</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Пинтер Шандор is a police official identified as the orchestrator of the car bomb assassination of Борош Томаш and allegedly responsible for the false prosecution of the speaker in 2017.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Рогоч">
  <data key="d0">Рогоч</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Рогоч is an individual who manufactured bombs and detonated the car bomb that killed Борош Томаш. He received a life sentence in Hungary and Slovakia, and chose to serve his sentence in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Портик">
  <data key="d0">Портик</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Портик is an individual who passed information from Пинтер Шандор to Рогоч, acting as an intermediary in the chain of command related to the assassination.&lt;SEP&gt;Портик is a person who worked with Шандор Пинтер and was imprisoned for connections to the criminal world in the 1990s.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Polish Fiat">
  <data key="d0">Polish Fiat</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Polish Fiat is a vehicle left abandoned in Budapest, later loaded with explosives and used to assassinate Борош Томаш by remote detonation as he passed by.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936108</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="1996">
  <data key="d0">1996</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">1996 is the year when the speaker began delivering money to Dietmar Klaud.&lt;SEP&gt;1996 is the year when the assassination of Борош Томаш occurred, according to the speaker’s recollection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="2010">
  <data key="d0">2010</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">2010 is the year when Орбан first won elections, leading to increased political power and subsequent retaliation against the speaker.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="2017">
  <data key="d0">2017</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">2017 is the year when the speaker was falsely imprisoned for seven years, allegedly as retaliation for knowing incriminating information about Орбан.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Шандор Пинтер">
  <data key="d0">Шандор Пинтер</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Шандор Пинтер was the head of Hungary’s police force and later became Hungary’s Minister of the Interior. He collaborated with Семён Могилевич and Игорь Король, accepting bribes to cover up criminal activities committed by Ukrainian criminals.&lt;SEP&gt;Шандор Пинтер is a former chief of police and later Minister of Interior of Hungary, who initially associated with criminal figures but later pursued them aggressively after assuming ministerial office.&lt;SEP&gt;Шандор Пинтер is the Minister of the Interior of Hungary, who is described as the highest superior of the individuals visiting the speaker in prison and is suspected of manipulating the situation for information extraction.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Сомбатхе">
  <data key="d0">Сомбатхе</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Сомбатхе is a prison location in Hungary, approximately 250 km from Budapest, where the speaker was initially detained and visited regularly by individuals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Вад">
  <data key="d0">Вад</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Вад is a location near Budapest, Hungary, where the speaker was transferred and received even more frequent visits from the individuals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Полиграф">
  <data key="d0">Полиграф</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Полиграф is a polygraph device used to assess the truthfulness of the speaker’s statements; the speaker underwent testing and was deemed to have told the full truth with 100% accuracy.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Шандер Пинтер">
  <data key="d0">Шандер Пинтер</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Шандер Пинтер is a person with whom the speaker frequently met and to whom a leather bag was delivered.&lt;SEP&gt;Шандер Пинтер is an alternate spelling or phonetic rendering of Шандор Пинтер, the Minister of the Interior of Hungary, referenced in the speaker’s statements regarding polygraph testing and authority.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Igor Koryol">
  <data key="d0">Igor Koryol</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Igor Koryol is the central figure who facilitated the speaker’s access to Dietmar Klaud and others, and with whom the speaker eventually had a falling out.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Koryol is a criminal figure who led a Ukrainian criminal group in Budapest, involved in protection rackets and entertainment venues, and had close ties with the translator and a higher-ranking criminal boss named Semyon Mogilevich.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Semyon Mogilevich">
  <data key="d0">Semyon Mogilevich</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Semyon Mogilevich is a high-ranking criminal boss referred to as the "boss of all bosses," who controlled criminal activities in Budapest and mediated disputes between Ukrainian and Russian criminal groups after the collapse of the Soviet Union.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Leonid Stitsyura">
  <data key="d0">Leonid Stitsyura</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Leonid Stitsyura is a criminal figure who led one of two Ukrainian brigades in Budapest, operating alongside Igor Koryol’s group in protection rackets and control of entertainment venues.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Goldf Gim">
  <data key="d0">Goldf Gim</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Goldf Gim is a well-equipped gym located on Szent Károly út in Budapest where László Kócs later encountered Igor Korol and his associates.&lt;SEP&gt;Goldf Gim is a well-equipped gym located on Sent Kiray Utsyo in Budapest during the 1990s, where the translator first met Igor Koryol.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Czech Republic">
  <data key="d0">Czech Republic</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Czech Republic is a country where Ukrainian and Russian criminal groups extended their operations after the collapse of the Soviet Union, alongside Hungary, Slovakia, and Ukraine.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Black Skull">
  <data key="d0">Black Skull</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Black Skull is an earlier criminal group in Budapest during the late 1980s, which transferred leadership to Igor Koryol, marking the rise of his criminal organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b107034176b638d6ed0508c3346f0725</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Mikhail Murashko">
  <data key="d0">Mikhail Murashko</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Mikhail Murashko is the Minister of Health of Russia who signed the 12-point cooperation agreement with Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1d17587159dea209c75a0ae5875a4b1</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\135.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Roman Dobrokhотов">
  <data key="d0">Roman Dobrokhотов</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Roman Dobrokhотов is the chief editor of The Insider and the host of a program discussing corruption and crime in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="László Kócs">
  <data key="d0">László Kócs</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">László Kócs is a professional bodybuilder who moved to Hungary in the mid-1990s, ran a legal alcohol distribution business, and had a confrontational encounter with Igor Korol.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Igor Korol">
  <data key="d0">Igor Korol</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Igor Korol is a figure associated with organized crime in Hungary who confronted László Kócs, demonstrated violent behavior, and later attempted to recruit him.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Alexander Kirichanin">
  <data key="d0">Alexander Kirichanin</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alexander Kirichanin is the childhood friend of László Kócs who co-founded a business selling alcohol and beverages in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936110</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tiszókecske">
  <data key="d0">Tiszókecske</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Tiszókecske is a small town near Kecskemét where László Kócs and Alexander Kirichanin purchased alcohol for distribution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936111</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Szent Károly út">
  <data key="d0">Szent Károly út</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Szent Károly út is the street in Budapest where the gym Goldf Gim is located, a place where László Kócs interacted with Igor Korol.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936111</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="1994">
  <data key="d0">1994</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">1994 is the year when László Kócs moved to Hungary and began his alcohol distribution business.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936111</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="1995">
  <data key="d0">1995</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">1995 is the year when László Kócs first met Igor Korol in Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936111</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="1998">
  <data key="d0">1998</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">1998 is the year when the alcohol distribution business ended due to Ukraine establishing a state monopoly on alcoholic beverages.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936111</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Kecskemét">
  <data key="d0">Kecskemét</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Kecskemét is a city in Hungary near Tiszókecske, referenced as the location from which alcohol was sourced by László Kócs and Alexander Kirichanin’s business. relation László Kócs Kecskemét business proximity László Kócs sourced alcohol near Kecskemét, specifically from the nearby town of Tiszókecske, as part of his distribution business in Hungary. relation Alexander Kirichanin Kecskemét business proximity Alexander Kirichanin operated his alcohol distribution business in proximity to Kecskemét, sourcing products from Tiszókecske. relation Igor Korol Szent Károly út territorial control Igor Korol and his associates were active at Szent Károly út, where Goldf Gim was located, indicating his influence over that area of Budapest. relation László Kócs Szent Károly út location of repeated interaction László Kócs encountered Igor Korol again at Szent Károly út, specifically at Goldf Gim, reinforcing their connection beyond the initial confrontation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Арбанк">
  <data key="d0">Арбанк</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Арбанк is a political figure who came to power after the elections in 1998, and is referenced as having sponsors, including Семён Могилевич.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Семён Могилевич">
  <data key="d0">Семён Могилевич</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Семён Могилевич, also known as Сева, was a criminal figure involved in large-scale illicit business operations in the late 1980s and early 1990s, including fuel adulteration and tax evasion. He was not concerned with small-scale criminal activities and focused on higher-level operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Семён Могилевич is a person who had a harsh and hypocritical attitude toward others, and is believed by the speaker to have been a main sponsor of Арбанк.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Саша Киричанин">
  <data key="d0">Саша Киричанин</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Саша Киричанин is a businessman and childhood friend of the speaker, who had his car taken and was forced to pay money by Игорь.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Витька">
  <data key="d0">Витька</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Витька is a person referred to by the speaker as someone who was expected to act in accordance with the speaker’s expectations, and is understood to be another reference to Арбанк.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Дитмарклоудо">
  <data key="d0">Дитмарклоудо</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Дитмарклоудо is a German of Jewish origin who manufactured explosives and received money from the speaker starting in spring 1996.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Spring 1998 Elections">
  <data key="d0">Spring 1998 Elections</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Spring 1998 Elections were a political event in Hungary during which Арбанк came to power, triggering changes in personal and political relationships.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Spring 1996">
  <data key="d0">Spring 1996</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Spring 1996 marks the beginning of regular money deliveries to Дитмарклоудо by the speaker.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Explosion near McDonalds in Budapest">
  <data key="d0">Explosion near McDonalds in Budapest</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The explosion near McDonald’s in Budapest is an event speculated by the speaker to be linked to Дитмарклоудо’s bomb-making activities, though the timing is uncertain.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Leather Bag">
  <data key="d0">Leather Bag</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The leather bag is an object used by the speaker to deliver money to Витька and Шандер Пинтер during regular meetings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Томаш Портик">
  <data key="d0">Томаш Портик</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Томаш Портик was a criminal associate involved in the illicit fuel business alongside Шандор Пинтер and Семён Могилевич. He is expected to remain in prison due to being targeted by Пинтер for elimination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936112</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Oyki Kish">
  <data key="d0">Oyki Kish</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Oyki Kish was the Hungarian term for the illicit business operation involving the adulteration of diesel fuel with dye, smuggling it into Hungary as heating oil to evade taxes, then extracting the dye and selling it as diesel fuel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Skoda">
  <data key="d0">Skoda</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Skoda was the make of vehicle used in bribe deliveries, typically dark blue or white, used for meetings between Игорь Король and Шандор Пинтер on a street corner in Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Шандера Птефи">
  <data key="d0">Шандера Птефи</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Шандера Птефи is a street corner in Budapest where bribe deliveries between Игорь Король and Шандор Пинтер regularly took place, typically involving a Skoda vehicle. relation Шандор Пинтер Шандера Птефи location of transaction, criminal meeting point Шандор Пинтер regularly met with Игорь Король at the corner of Шандера Птефи to receive bribes, making it a key location for criminal coordination in Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Бухарест">
  <data key="d0">Бухарест</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Бухарест is a city where Игорь Король attempted to invest money in a casino before being deported from Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Киев">
  <data key="d0">Киев</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Киев is a city that was offered as an alternative destination to Игорь Король during his deportation from Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936113</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Израиль">
  <data key="d0">Израиль</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Израиль is the country where Леонид Тюра became a citizen after serving time in prison in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
