<node id="Немзтведелмилгат">
  <data key="d0">Немзтведелмилгат</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Немзтведелмилгат is the full name of the organization abbreviated as НВС, described as a national interest protection unit analogous to an internal KGB. relation НВС Немзтведелмилгат abbreviation,identity НВС is the abbreviated form of Немзтведелмилгат, referring to the same organization created by Пинтер Шандер.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-85ab176e3cbddf97c2d5cd15191ff861</data>
