  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Nedits Maraklodu is a person suspected by the speaker of being involved in the explosion in Budapest, though this is described as speculative.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e</data>
