  <data key="d0">Alexander Kirichenko</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Alexander Kirichenko is a person connected to the speaker’s childhood home and a Ukrainian city mayor, referenced in the context of a falling out with Igor Koryol.</data>
