<node id="Orvónky">
  <data key="d0">Orvónky</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Orvónky is a location in central Budapest where the explosion reportedly occurred. entity Szentendre location Szentendre is a small city near Budapest where Dietmar Klaud lived in a large house and where the speaker met him to deliver money. entity Kirichenko, Alexander person Alexander Kirichenko is a person connected to the speaker’s childhood home and a Ukrainian city mayor, referenced in the context of a falling out with Igor Koryol. relation István Hofman Budapest location of attack István Hofman was bombed in Budapest, with the attack occurring one week after the death of József Pristash. relation Dietmar Klaud Szentendre residence Dietmar Klaud resided in a large house in Szentendre, where the speaker delivered money to him. relation Alexander Kirichenko Igor Koryol conflict,personal dispute The falling out between the speaker and Igor Koryol involved Alexander Kirichenko and the speaker’s childhood home, linked to a Ukrainian city mayor. relation Igor Koryol Budapest operational base Igor Koryol operated in Budapest, facilitating money deliveries and connections to figures such as Dietmar Klaud and István Hofman. relation József Pristash Budapest location of death József Pristash was killed in Budapest, shortly before the bombing of his associate István Hofman.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
