</node>
<node id="Donald Tusk">
  <data key="d0">Donald Tusk</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Donald Tusk is the Prime Minister of Poland who criticized the proposal as exceeding the bounds of what is shocking.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Tusk is the Prime Minister of Poland who publicly responded to the leaked transcript by questioning Viktor Orbán’s alignment with Putin and challenging Jarosław Kaczyński on whether he supports Orbán’s stance.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Tusk is the Prime Minister of Poland who publicly acknowledged that EU member states avoid discussing sensitive issues in full council formats due to concerns about leaks to Moscow via Hungarian officials.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9360bf859acb934b8ebad024d1c18290&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3aab01d8a12e8135d55b3153fc006d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43</data>
