  <data key="d5">1777936496</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Minister of Viktor Orban">
  <data key="d0">Minister of Viktor Orban</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The minister of Viktor Orban is the individual who proposed sending European Union documents to Sergey Lavrov through the Hungarian embassy in Moscow. relation Minister of Viktor Orban Sergey Lavrov diplomatic communication The minister of Viktor Orban proposed sending European Union documents to Sergey Lavrov. relation Minister of Viktor Orban European Union document origin The minister of Viktor Orban initiated the transmission of European Union documents. relation Minister of Viktor Orban Hungary official representation The minister of Viktor Orban acts as an official representative of Hungary in this diplomatic action. relation Hungarian Embassy in Moscow Sergey Lavrov diplomatic delivery channel The Hungarian embassy in Moscow was designated as the channel through which European Union documents were to be delivered to Sergey Lavrov. relation Hungarian Embassy in Moscow European Union diplomatic intermediary The Hungarian embassy in Moscow served as the intermediary for delivering European Union documents to Sergey Lavrov.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9360bf859acb934b8ebad024d1c18290</data>
