  <data key="d0">Adriatic Pipeline</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The Adriatic Pipeline (JANAF) is an infrastructure project that has demonstrated its capacity to deliver gas reliably to Hungarian and Slovakian markets.</data>
