<node id="JANAF">
  <data key="d0">JANAF</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">JANAF is the acronym for the Adriatic Pipeline, which has demonstrated its capacity to deliver gas reliably to Hungarian and Slovakian markets. relation JANAF Adriatic Pipeline acronym, equivalent designation JANAF is the acronym used in the text to refer to the Adriatic Pipeline, indicating they are the same infrastructure project.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-69d93e1cd4546542fd7a6dd43a3e688d</data>
