  <data key="d0">Mehyigorye</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Mehyigorye is the luxurious residence of former Ukrainian president Viktor Yanukovych, which journalists compared to the Hatvanpusta estate, to the detriment of Viktor Orbán’s public image.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fc1feb8e698e39594612de628b9b30f8</data>
