  <data key="d0">Gabrielius Landsbergis</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Gabrielius Landsbergis is the former Minister of Foreign Affairs of Lithuania who confirmed that EU diplomats have long understood the risk of information leaks from Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43</data>
