<node id="Madjar">
  <data key="d0">Madjar</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Madjar is a Hungarian political figure who publicly condemned Russian interference by demanding the expulsion of Russian intelligence officers and invoking historical anti-Soviet slogans.&lt;SEP&gt;Madjar is a political opponent of Orbán, referenced in a hypothetical scenario involving a recorded conversation with Weber.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3da3b046ca1fff9119eaf735e34f56d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce845ea082895ffef253ac499ba46794</data>
