<node id="Doppelganger">
  <data key="d0">Doppelganger</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Doppelganger is the codename for a disinformation operation conducted by Social Design Agency, involving the creation of fake Western news websites targeting Ukraine, as referenced in the source text. relation Social Design Agency United States sanction, disinformation operation The United States imposed sanctions on Social Design Agency in 2024 for its role in the Doppelganger operation, which involved creating fake Western news sites with disinformation against Ukraine. relation Russia Moldova electoral interference, information warfare Russia conducted information warfare in Moldova through voter suppression networks and disinformation campaigns aimed at preventing Sándu’s re-election. relation Social Design Agency Moldova disinformation, covert operation Social Design Agency coordinated disinformation operations in Moldova using the same methods later applied in Hungary, including fake accounts and influencer manipulation. relation GRU Russia subordinate unit, intelligence structure GRU is a Russian military intelligence unit operating under the authority of the Russian state, with officers embedded in diplomatic missions to conduct covert influence operations. relation SVR Russia subordinate unit, intelligence structure SVR is the Russian foreign intelligence service operating under the authority of the Russian state, responsible for drafting the "Gamechanger" plan targeting Hungary. relation Orbán European Union political conflict, sovereignty dispute The Russian disinformation campaign portrays Orbán as defending Hungarian sovereignty against the European Union, framing Brussels as a controlling force undermining Hungary. relation Madjar European Union political alignment, pro-Western stance Madjar’s condemnation of Russian interference aligns with pro-Western political positions, implicitly supporting European Union values and institutions. relation Fides European Union political tension, sovereignty conflict Fides is portrayed in Russian disinformation as resisting European Union influence, with the campaign framing EU institutions as hostile to Hungarian sovereignty. relation Russia Hungary historical reference, political analogy Russian interference operations in Hungary deliberately evoke historical memory of the 1956 anti-Soviet uprising, using Madjar’s slogan to imply Orbán is a Soviet-style puppet. relation Washington Post European Union intelligence collaboration, source sharing The Washington Post’s report relied on documents intercepted and verified by European intelligence services, indicating collaboration between EU agencies and U.S. media. relation Financial Times European Union intelligence collaboration, source sharing The Financial Times cited documents provided by European intelligence services to report on Social Design Agency’s operations in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3da3b046ca1fff9119eaf735e34f56d4</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777936517</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
