<node id="Ground News">
  <data key="d0">Ground News</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Ground News is a platform offering tools to analyze media bias and compare how the same news is covered across the political spectrum.&lt;SEP&gt;Ground News is a media platform sponsored in the video that provides analysis of media bias and is promoted as a tool for understanding how news stories are framed.&lt;SEP&gt;Ground News is a sponsor of the video described in the source text.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2369463d8ede9e477cfaf832815ef3c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6bcd039eb9ab628a1ffb566a855dd2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1561937403235278917e112e7843f5b0</data>
