<node id="2026 Hungarian Elections">
  <data key="d0">2026 Hungarian Elections</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The 2026 Hungarian Elections are the upcoming national elections where Fidesz redrew district boundaries and introduced electoral changes to favor its electoral performance.&lt;SEP&gt;The 2026 Hungarian elections are the upcoming electoral event in which electoral district boundaries were redrawn to eliminate two opposition-leaning constituencies, benefiting Fidesz.&lt;SEP&gt;The 2026 Hungarian Elections are a political event where Viktor Orbán’s Fidesz party faces strong opposition from Tisza, with the outcome still uncertain despite polling trends.&lt;SEP&gt;The 2026 Hungarian Elections were a parliamentary vote in which Tisza won a constitutional majority, leading to the defeat of Orbán and Fidesz, influenced by leaked conversations with Russia.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2369463d8ede9e477cfaf832815ef3c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6bcd039eb9ab628a1ffb566a855dd2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-867b81690ecba5bc75830acd44c39131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a810084503e65cb067ff1fc3c7a05189</data>
