  <data key="d0">2014 Hungarian Political Campaign</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The 2014 Hungarian political campaign involved accusations of foreign financing as a propaganda tool used by Viktor Orbán to maintain power.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2369463d8ede9e477cfaf832815ef3c5</data>
