  <data key="d0">Hungarian State Media</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Hungarian State Media is a network controlled by Fidesz that dominates 90% of media outlets in Hungary, including television, radio, newspapers, and outdoor advertising, and is used to spread disinformation.</data>
