  <data key="d0">Artificial Intelligence</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Artificial Intelligence is used by Hungarian state media to generate fake images and videos, such as depicting opposition leaders as dogs on leashes or fabricating protest scenes to mislead voters.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2369463d8ede9e477cfaf832815ef3c5</data>
