  <data key="d0">Serbia–Hungary Gas Pipeline</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Serbia–Hungary gas pipeline is an energy corridor critical to Hungary’s infrastructure, where explosive devices were discovered shortly before elections, triggering geopolitical tensions.</data>
