  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Breitbart is a right-wing media outlet that emphasizes Orbán’s claim that Ukraine may be behind the attack on the Serbia–Hungary gas pipeline.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6bcd039eb9ab628a1ffb566a855dd2b</data>
