  <data key="d0">J.D. Vance</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">J.D. Vance is the Vice President of the United States who visited Budapest to support Viktor Orbán’s regime shortly before the Hungarian elections.&lt;SEP&gt;J.D. Vance is the U.S. vice president who visited Budapest to campaign for Viktor Orbán.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1561937403235278917e112e7843f5b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4219648b35dcbd430c607633467c92dc</data>
