<node id="Viktor Orbáns regime">
  <data key="d0">Viktor Orbáns regime</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Viktor Orbán’s regime refers to the political system in Hungary under Viktor Orbán’s leadership, characterized by electoral manipulation, corruption, and alignment with foreign powers such as Russia and the United States.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1561937403235278917e112e7843f5b0</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\142.txt</data>
