</node>
<node id="Opposition">
  <data key="d0">Opposition</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The opposition in Hungary is portrayed in Russian disinformation campaigns as Western puppets seeking to start a nuclear war, and is depicted as being systematically disadvantaged by Fides’s control of state resources and media.&lt;SEP&gt;Opposition is a political group in Hungary that held rallies with tens of thousands of Hungarian attendees chanting slogans against Russians and demanding Orbán's departure. relation Opposition Hungary rally,political protest The Opposition held rallies in Hungary where tens of thousands of attendees chanted "Russians, go home!" and criticized Orbán. relation Opposition Orbán criticism,antagonism At Opposition rallies in Hungary, attendees directed insults and demands for Orbán to leave, indicating direct antagonism toward him.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1561937403235278917e112e7843f5b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-765485889ec9c96686562866ad272ef6</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\142.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\159.txt</data>
