  <data key="d0">EU Made Simple</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">EU Made Simple is a media channel that produced the video content analyzing Viktor Orbán’s electoral tactics and the state of democracy in Hungary; it advocates for voter mobilization and European Union reform.</data>
