<node id="Pest">
  <data key="d0">Pest</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Pest is the region surrounding Budapest, which had 12 districts in 2022 and fully voted for Fidesz; two new districts were added for the 2026 elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Pest is a region in Hungary, where the highest voter turnout during the elections was recorded at 69.67%.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-867b81690ecba5bc75830acd44c39131&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e4bedfc173098465d955c0364c5de9b</data>
