  <data key="d2">Слава Украине is a slogan referenced in the text as being opposed by Hungarian officials. entity Слава Венгрии other Слава Венгрии is a slogan used by Viktor Orbán in response to "Слава Украине". relation Viktor Orbán Слава Украине rejection, slogan response Viktor Orbán rejects the slogan "Слава Украине" by countering with "Слава Венгрии". relation Viktor Orbán Слава Венгрии promotion, slogan endorsement Viktor Orbán promotes the slogan "Слава Венгрии" as an alternative to "Слава Украине".</data>
