<node id="Kim Jong Un">
  <data key="d0">Kim Jong Un</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Kim Jong Un is the supreme leader of North Korea, who has consolidated power through a combination of familial succession and strict control over state institutions. He has publicly reaffirmed North Korea’s support for Russia’s invasion of Ukraine, framing it as a “holy war” and pledging assistance to Moscow in achieving victory. In alignment with this stance, he has congratulated North Korean soldiers fighting alongside Russian forces and inaugurated a residential complex in Pyongyang for the families of deceased soldiers, while also inspecting plans for a monument and museum dedicated to their memory. To honor these sacrifices, he compelled high-ranking officials from the Workers’ Party and the Ministry of Defense to personally maintain the graves of fallen soldiers and plant lawns at memorial sites. Kim Jong Un has also mobilized North Korean youth, urging them to prepare for war in Ukraine as the vanguard of the party and a key force for state objectives. In a move underscoring the militarization and dynastic nature of his regime, he appointed his 13-year-old daughter to lead an agency responsible for missile production, and in another report, to head North Korea’s nuclear forces—indicating the potential succession of nuclear authority within his family. His leadership is characterized by an aggressive ideological alignment with Russia, domestic propaganda glorifying military sacrifice, and the entrenchment of a hereditary autocracy, leading global analysts to view him as a destabilizing figure whose actions threaten international stability if not opposed.&lt;SEP&gt;Kim Jong Un is the leader of North Korea, whose personal behavior, such as not taking his daughter to an aquapark, is referenced as an indicator of regime dynamics.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1704b3bc09f596547c35a95941e29e5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1769d39ef03a8083db256740e9cd0766&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce8f15f650ac7d354598ceb3c44ee55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2cd9eaecb1b87407745fb11b4c0a1b5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8262c667cbee1913092248cf832b5b2d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe4a537b10e5a1cd6b9731ae8a2ee0a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a32816fdb3610e6d8a54bb67883ce674&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-407b20f30b0250ff3bfa0029af7e723c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-182d3ae7e14d1083d21cb4dce15639d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b081d06450863ed7e420f49361e136e9</data>
