<node id="Donald Trump Jr.">
  <data key="d0">Donald Trump Jr.</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Donald Trump Jr. is a person who appealed to Hungarians to support Viktor Orbán, referring to him as a friend and ally of his father. entity Viktor Orbán person Viktor Orbán is a Hungarian political leader who was endorsed by Donald Trump Jr. as a pro-Hungary candidate and a direct ally to the White House. entity Hungary country Hungary is the country where Viktor Orbán is a political leader and to which Donald Trump Jr. directed his appeal for support. entity White House location White House is the official residence and workplace of the President of the United States, which Donald Trump Jr. claims Viktor Orbán has a direct line to. entity European Union organization European Union is the organization implicitly referenced by Donald Trump Jr. as the broader context in which Viktor Orbán is positioned as a unique leader. relation Donald Trump Jr. Viktor Orbán endorsement,political alliance Donald Trump Jr. directly appealed to Hungarians to support Viktor Orbán, calling him a friend and ally of his father and the only European leader with a direct line to the White House. relation Viktor Orbán Hungary leadership,political representation Viktor Orbán is the political leader of Hungary whom Donald Trump Jr. urged Hungarians to vote for as a champion of Hungarian independence. relation Viktor Orbán White House diplomatic connection,political alignment Donald Trump Jr. claimed that Viktor Orbán has a direct line to the White House, indicating a close political alignment between Orbán and the U.S. administration led by his father. relation Hungary European Union political distinction,alignment Donald Trump Jr. contrasted Viktor Orbán’s stance with the broader European Union context, implying Orbán represents an independent alternative within Europe.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3f9c193424dde3d5eaae9c7403580444</data>
