<node id="Semen Mogilevich">
  <data key="d0">Semen Mogilevich</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Semen Mogilevich, known as "The Brainy Don," is a criminal figure with an estimated net worth exceeding $10 billion; he controlled major military and defense companies in Hungary, participated in Russia-Ukraine energy trade, allegedly sold weapons to Al-Qaeda, financed enriched uranium sales to terrorists, and laundered money through New York Stock Exchange companies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777937148</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sandor Pinter">
  <data key="d0">Sandor Pinter</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Sandor Pinter is the current Hungarian Minister of Internal Affairs who, while serving as head of Budapest police, received large sums of money from Semen Mogilevich.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777937148</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dithmar Clodo">
  <data key="d0">Dithmar Clodo</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Dithmar Clodo is a longtime associate of Semen Mogilevich who served as a mercenary in Rhodesia and Afghanistan, was convicted for bombings in Hungary in the 1990s, extradited to Germany for serious crimes, and delivered bribes to Hungarian officials on Mogilevich’s orders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777937148</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="David Bogatin">
  <data key="d0">David Bogatin</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">David Bogatin is an associate of Semen Mogilevich who, in 1984, purchased five luxury apartments in Trump Tower for $6 million in cash, initiating a money laundering operation through Trump’s real estate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777937148</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="FSB">
  <data key="d0">FSB</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The FSB is the Russian federal security service that received compromising videos of Viktor Orbán from Semen Mogilevich in exchange for protection from tax investigations.&lt;SEP&gt;FSB is the Russian federal security service, suspected in the input text of having a connection to Orbán, though not confirmed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ccbba289defe85bee861c66ae67de11</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt&lt;SEP&gt;D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\173.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1778011265</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
  <data key="d7">FSB</data>
</node>
<node id="FBI">
  <data key="d0">FBI</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The FBI is the United States federal law enforcement agency that investigated Semen Mogilevich and alleged his involvement in arms trafficking, terrorism financing, and money laundering.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
  <data key="d4">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\165.txt</data>
  <data key="d5">1777937149</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trump Tower">
  <data key="d0">Trump Tower</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Trump Tower is a building located at 721 Fifth Avenue in New York City, where David Bogatin met Donald Trump and purchased luxury apartments used for money laundering.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5ccdb895c49cc5a1b4f5807c901e88cf</data>
