<node id="Hungarian electoral system">
  <data key="d0">Hungarian electoral system</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">The Hungarian electoral system is a mixed proportional-majoritarian system where votes for losing candidates in majoritarian districts are transferred to their party's proportional list, and winners receive a bonus based on the vote difference with the second-place candidate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8c1110bd39ddbd2f60dff21ab98ff641</data>
