  <data key="d0">Dmitry Peskov</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Dmitry Peskov is the spokesperson for the Russian president who declared that Russia would not congratulate Peter Magyar on his electoral victory and labeled Hungary as a “hostile country.”</data>
