  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Szijjártó–Lavrov Series refers to a collection of leaked conversations from 2024–2025 involving assistance in lifting sanctions on Russian oligarchs, coordination on Ukraine, and leakage of internal EU documents.</data>
