<node id="Electoral Code Amendment">
  <data key="d0">Electoral Code Amendment</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Electoral Code Amendment is a proposed legislative bill in Slovakia, prepared by Robert Fico’s government, that includes multiple changes to electoral rules to favor his party and reduce opposition representation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-09de750ab096b64385f95a95c7d0e5ad</data>
