  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">Chinese Fishing Vessel is a vessel that violated South Korea's territorial waters and was boarded by South Korea's coast guard. relation South Korea Chinese Fishing Vessel boarding,territorial enforcement South Korea's coast guard conducted a boarding operation on the Chinese Fishing Vessel for violating territorial waters.</data>
