<node id="Kursk Oblast">
  <data key="d0">Kursk Oblast</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Kursk Oblast is a location where KNA mercenaries were eliminated, as referenced in the concert held in North Korea. relation North Korea Kursk Oblast commemoration,geographical connection North Korea held a concert in memory of KNA mercenaries who were eliminated in the Kursk Oblast.&lt;SEP&gt;Kursk Oblast is a region in Russia where North Korean soldiers reportedly died during military operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Kursk Oblast is a location where North Korean soldiers were killed, as referenced in the memorial complex opened by North Korea.</data>
