<node id="Северная Корея">
  <data key="d0">Северная Корея</data>
  <data key="d1">country</data>
  <data key="d2">Северная Корея is the country referred to in the source text as planning to export pharmaceuticals to Russia; it is synonymous with КНДР. relation Северная Корея Russia pharmaceutical supply,strategic partnership Северная Корея plans to export pharmaceuticals to Россия, as reported in the source text, which is framed within the context of their comprehensive strategic partnership since mid-2024. relation Северная Корея Kremlin strategic cooperation,quid pro quo The export of pharmaceuticals from Северная Корея to Россия is suggested as a form of gratitude to the Kremlin for military support in the conflict against Ukraine. relation Северная Корея Ukraine conflict involvement,indirect support Северная Корея’s cooperation with Россия is interpreted as indirect support in the conflict against Ukraine, per the source text.&lt;SEP&gt;Северная Корея provided military assistance to Russia, supplied weapons and military personnel between August 2023 and December 2025, and experienced economic growth in 2024 due to military cooperation with Russia.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e5d2b942a2c7c68f8c9998675a0bad2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f525f78f89f5b96d8fc7535b3303ae6b</data>
