  <data key="d0">Северокорейские войска</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">Северокорейские войска are North Korean military units operating in Russia, participating in combat actions in the Kursk Oblast of Russia, conducting artillery strikes against Ukrainian border areas, and performing aerial and artillery reconnaissance and fire correction under Russian command.</data>
