<node id="Ким Чен Ын">
  <data key="d0">Ким Чен Ын</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Ким Чен Ын is the leader of North Korea who aims to modernize the country’s armed forces by gaining practical combat experience in Ukraine, particularly in drone technology and high-intensity warfare tactics.&lt;SEP&gt;Ким Чен Ын is the leader of Северная Корея who strategically aligned with Vladimir Putin and signed a mutual military assistance treaty.&lt;SEP&gt;Ким Чен Ын is the leader of North Korea, referenced in the input text as the subject of a statement that a suspected North Korean hacker refused to utter during an interview. entity North Korean hacker other A suspected North Korean hacker was exposed during an interview for refusing to say a derogatory statement about Ким Чен Ын. relation North Korean hacker Ким Чен Ын refusal,loyalty,test The suspected North Korean hacker refused to utter a derogatory statement about Ким Чен Ын during an interview, indicating loyalty or adherence to the North Korean leadership.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec36c3f34e874fb6a0c44b533c707cfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f525f78f89f5b96d8fc7535b3303ae6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef573f6547db918e0c04e9db6d87c22b</data>
