</node>
<node id="Korean People's Army">
  <data key="d0">Korean People's Army</data>
  <data key="d1">military_unit</data>
  <data key="d2">The Korean People's Army is the official military force of North Korea, of which the North Korean troops operating in Ukraine are a deployed contingent. relation Korean People's Army Северокорейские войска commanding, organizational parent The Korean People's Army is the official military organization to which Северокорейские войска belong as its deployed units in Ukraine. relation Северокорейские войска Korean People's Army deployed unit, subordinate force Северокорейские войска are a deployed contingent of the Korean People's Army, operating under its command structure and strategic direction.&lt;SEP&gt;Korean People's Army is the military force of North Korea whose soldiers have been deployed for artillery strikes, drone reconnaissance, demining, and construction work in support of Russian operations.&lt;SEP&gt;Korean People's Army is the military force of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, celebrating its 78th anniversary, with soldiers actively engaged in combat in Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;The Korean People's Army is the military force of North Korea from which generals provide briefings to Kim Jong Un's daughter. relation Kim Jong Un's Daughter Korean People's Army command,briefing Kim Jong Un's daughter receives briefings from generals and occasionally issues orders, indicating command authority over the Korean People's Army's nuclear forces.&lt;SEP&gt;Korean People's Army is the military force of North Korea whose fallen soldiers are commemorated in the memorial complex opened in North Korea. relation Russia Korean People's Army equipment transfer,honor Russia provided trophy equipment to North Korea for exhibition honoring the fallen soldiers of the Korean People's Army.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec36c3f34e874fb6a0c44b533c707cfe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f539231f0337d24e0f7782691b6fac00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fce8f15f650ac7d354598ceb3c44ee55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe4a537b10e5a1cd6b9731ae8a2ee0a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7c66fd004b5169922bcb617129ac236</data>
