  <data key="d2">Japan is the country represented by its Minister of Defense, Shinzo Koizumi, who made a statement regarding the war in Ukraine. relation Shinzo Koizumi Japan government position, official role Shinzo Koizumi is the Minister of Defense of Japan, indicating his official role within the Japanese government.</data>
