  <data key="d0">Reuters</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Reuters is a news organization that reported on Kim Jong Un's inauguration of the Sebel residential complex and the deployment of North Korean soldiers to Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Reuters is a news agency that reported on Kim Jong Un's call for North Korean youth to prepare for war in Ukraine on the side of Russia. relation Kim Jong Un Reuters media reporting,statement Kim Jong Un's statement regarding North Korean youth participating in the war in Ukraine was reported by Reuters.</data>
