  <data key="d0">Agency for Missile Production</data>
  <data key="d1">other</data>
  <data key="d2">An agency responsible for missile production in North Korea, now led by Kim Ju Ae, with authority superseding its formal head Zhang Chang He. relation Kim Ju Ae Agency for Missile Production leadership, command Kim Ju Ae was appointed to lead the agency responsible for missile production, assuming direct authority over its operations and personnel.</data>
