  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Keir Starmer is the Prime Minister of the United Kingdom who advocates for the UK's participation in the Security Action for Europe (SAFE) fund and promotes deeper European defense and economic cooperation.&lt;SEP&gt;Keir Starmer is the leader of the United Kingdom who has refused U.S. requests to use British military bases for initial strikes against Iran, leading to diplomatic friction with Donald Trump.</data>
