<edge source="United States" target="Viktor Orbán">
  <data key="d8">4.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The United States, through Secretary of State Marco Rubio and Vice President Vance, has publicly supported Viktor Orbán during his electoral campaign.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán receives direct political support from the United States, exemplified by Vice President J.D. Vance’s visit to Budapest to endorse his regime before the elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán has a friendly relationship with the United States, specifically through his association with Donald Trump.&lt;SEP&gt;The United States, through Donald Trump, J.D. Vance, and Marco Rubio, actively supported Viktor Orbán ahead of the Hungarian election.</data>
  <data key="d10">alliance,diplomatic support,endorsement,foreign support,political alignment,political alliance,political support,public endorsement</data>
