  <data key="d8">3.0</data>
  <data key="d9">According to Алиса Вайдель, Donald Trump violated the sovereignty of Greenland, drawing a parallel to actions attributed to Vladimir Putin.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump threatened to annex Greenland, prompting reassessment by European far-right parties.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump made threats regarding Greenland, which heightened European concerns about U.S. reliability and influenced support for UK-EU defense integration.</data>
