<edge source="Donald Trump" target="Orbán">
  <data key="d8">5.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Orbán uses Donald Trump’s image to legitimize his policies, suggesting that even the United States under Trump now supports Hungary’s stance, reducing his international isolation.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán is compared to Donald Trump for using allegations of election fraud as a political defense.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán praised Donald Trump’s approach, comparing it to a tornado, and expressed admiration for his political stance.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán sought to host a meeting between Putin and Donald Trump in Budapest to gain political leverage before elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán is described as the main agent of Donald Trump, indicating a direct alignment or operational connection.</data>
  <data key="d10">agent,alignment,ideological alignment,political alignment,political opportunism,political strategy,political validation,praise,rhetorical comparison</data>
