  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Concerns about not angering Donald Trump influenced the European Union’s decision not to transfer frozen Russian assets to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump’s unpredictable actions, including threats toward Greenland and criticism of NATO, have increased European desire to include the United Kingdom in defense initiatives like SAFE.</data>
