<edge source="Donald Trump" target="Viktor Orbán">
  <data key="d8">6.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán responded to statements that Donald Trump's actions benefit Russia and reflect Putin's ambitions.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump praised Viktor Orbán as a fantastic leader, emphasized their excellent relationship, and stated he would not have called the rally if he did not believe Orbán was doing a good job.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump supports Viktor Orbán, and this endorsement is leveraged by Orbán’s campaign to bolster credibility among conservative Hungarian voters.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump is described as a friend of Viktor Orbán, indicating a political alignment between their ideologies and leadership styles.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump publicly endorses Viktor Orbán for re-election as Prime Minister of Hungary, expressing full and unconditional support and claiming to have supported him in 2022.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump indicates he would provide financial support to Hungary if Viktor Orbán wins the elections, implying endorsement of Orbán's leadership.</data>
  <data key="d10">alignment,alliance,criticism,electoral backing,endorsement,political alignment,political support,positive relationship,praise</data>
