<edge source="Donald Trump" target="Hungary">
  <data key="d8">4.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Donald Trump expressed love for Hungary and commended it for preserving its national identity and avoiding the immigration-related problems experienced by other countries.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump states that relations between the United States and Hungary have reached new heights of cooperation during his administration, largely due to Viktor Orbán's leadership.&lt;SEP&gt;Donald Trump's administration is prepared to deploy the economic potential of the United States to strengthen Hungary's economy if Viktor Orbán and the Hungarian people request it.&lt;SEP&gt;Russian media question whether Hungary might find Donald Trump's conservative approach more appealing than the European Union's stance.</data>
