<edge source="Russia" target="Putin">
  <data key="d8">3.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Putin represents Russia and responded to Orbán's inquiry on behalf of Russia, stating that Russia's reaction would be strong.&lt;SEP&gt;Putin is the leader of Russia and his sensitivities were factored into European Union policy decisions regarding frozen assets and Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Putin represents Russia in diplomatic efforts and is the central figure in its strategic approach to the war with Ukraine.</data>
