<edge source="Russia" target="Hungarian Government">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Hungarian Government's petition frames the Russia-Ukraine war as a conflict whose financial burden it opposes, implicitly acknowledging Russia's role in the conflict.</data>
