<edge source="Russia" target="Mukachevo">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Russia conducted a missile strike on Mukachevo, Ukraine, in August 2025, an event that the Hungarian government refused to explicitly condemn.</data>
  <data key="d10">military attack</data>
