<edge source="Russia" target="Slovakia">
  <data key="d8">3.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Slovakia did not condemn Russia for the strike on the Brody Pumping Station and claimed there were no technical reasons to halt fuel transit.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovakia opposes EU sanctions against Russia due to the Druzhba pipeline blockade by Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovakia maintains energy dependency on Russia via the Druzhba Pipeline, while facing geopolitical tension due to Robert Fico’s pro-Kremlin gestures.</data>
