<edge source="European Union" target="Brussels">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Brussels is the seat of the European Union's commission, which Viktor Orbán criticized for maintaining sanctions on Russian oil.&lt;SEP&gt;Brussels is the administrative center of the European Union, where its bureaucratic institutions are located and from which interference in Hungary is alleged to originate.</data>
