<edge source="European Union" target="Viktor Orban">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orban has actively sabotaged European Union policies, including blocking a 90 billion euro credit for Ukraine, and framed conflicts with the EU as existential battles for national sovereignty.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orban has repeatedly blocked EU sanctions and aid packages to Ukraine, claiming to defend Hungary’s national interests against EU dictates.</data>
  <data key="d10">policy sabotage,political conflict,political opposition,sanction blockade</data>
