</edge>
<edge source="European Union" target="18th Sanctions Package">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The European Union adopted the 18th Sanctions Package, which targets Russian companies and banks, though its effectiveness was reduced due to Siyarto's efforts.&lt;SEP&gt;The 18th Sanctions Package of the European Union was targeted for modification, with 72 entries removed due to lobbying by Siyarta and Russian officials, altering EU policy outcomes.</data>
  <data key="d10">adoption,implementation,policy manipulation,sanctions modification</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-1b346b60f2318d240edb84608cb2b374&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2843e721f5be37e2778dd3123cdcec43</data>
