  <data key="d13">1777936572</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="European Union" target="2Rivers">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The European Union planned to impose sanctions on 2Rivers, a Dubai-based company trading Russian oil, which Siyarto sought to prevent.</data>
  <data key="d10">sanctions target</data>
