<edge source="European Union" target="Jey D. Vens">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Jey D. Vens directly criticized the European Union's bureaucracy for its perceived meddling in Hungary’s elections and information space, calling it shameful.</data>
  <data key="d10">criticism,opposition to interference</data>
