<edge source="European Union" target="Sergey Lavrov">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">European Union documents were proposed to be delivered to Sergey Lavrov, indicating an attempt at official communication.&lt;SEP&gt;Sergey Lavrov sought documents from Péter Szijjártó to understand and potentially leverage Hungary’s stance against Ukraine’s EU accession, indicating alignment with Hungary’s strategic position.</data>
  <data key="d10">diplomatic document exchange,information gathering,strategic alignment</data>
