</edge>
<edge source="European Union" target="Orbán">
  <data key="d8">4.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Orbán’s refusal to implement EU-mandated reforms led the European Union to freeze approximately €18 billion in funding to Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán blocked the 20th EU sanctions package against Russia and the €90 billion EU credit line to Ukraine, directly opposing EU policy to support Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán is described as the primary destructive factor within the European Union, implying a destabilizing relationship.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán systematically distances Hungary from the European Union, weakening its institutional authority and cohesion.</data>
  <data key="d10">blockade,conflict,destabilization,distance,funding suspension,non-compliance,opposition,undermine,weaken</data>
