  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="European Union" target="2026–2027">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The €90 billion EU credit line intended for Ukraine in 2026–2027 was a planned financial commitment by the European Union to support Ukraine’s war effort and state stability.</data>
  <data key="d10">funding commitment,planned support</data>
