<edge source="European Union" target="Robert Fico">
  <data key="d8">5.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Robert Fico criticizes the European Union for hypocrisy and financial support to Ukraine, and declares Slovakia’s refusal to participate in the €90 billion war credit.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico is the prime minister of Slovakia, a member state of the European Union, and his overflight request involves other EU member states.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico previously signaled intent to block EU sanctions packages against Russia, particularly the 20th package, though he ultimately did not follow through.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico, as Prime Minister of Slovakia, represents a country that has undergone Euro-integration and is offering its experience to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico endorsed Ukraine's membership in the European Union.</data>
