  <data key="d9">Ukraine controls access to the Druzhba pipeline, and its refusal to permit inspections undermines Orbán’s strategy to force concessions.&lt;SEP&gt;Ukraine blocked the operation of the Druzhba pipeline, which triggered Hungary's financial retaliation and statements by its minister.&lt;SEP&gt;Ukraine is accused of disrupting the operation of the Druzhba oil pipeline, cutting off energy supplies to Slovakia and Hungary.</data>
