  <data key="d8">3.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Druzhba Pipeline’s disruption caused by a Russian attack resulted in the cessation of emergency electricity supplies to Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Ukraine blocked the Druzhba Pipeline, which influenced Slovakia's stance on EU sanctions against Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Ukraine is falsely accused by Orbán of deliberately failing to repair the Druzhba Pipeline, despite the damage being caused by a Russian strike.</data>
