<edge source="Ukraine" target="Budapest">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Budapest served as a hub for criminal activities carried out by Ukrainian gangs, with frequent violent crimes and bribes paid to Hungarian officials to ensure impunity.&lt;SEP&gt;After the Soviet Union’s collapse, Ukrainian criminal groups migrated to Budapest, establishing strong operational networks in its entertainment and nightlife sectors.</data>
