<edge source="Ukraine" target="North Korea">
  <data key="d8">6.0</data>
  <data key="d9">North Korean military personnel have participated in combat operations against Ukraine as part of Russian forces, acquiring frontline warfare experience.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korean soldiers have conducted artillery strikes, including from artillery and multiple rocket launchers, against Ukraine from Russian territory.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korean soldiers were deployed to fight against Ukraine, with nearly half estimated to have been killed in combat operations there.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korean soldiers have died in Ukraine in what is described as an illegal aggressive war, making Ukraine a direct victim of North Korea’s involvement.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korean soldiers died in a war against Ukraine, as stated in the directive issued by Kim Jong Un.&lt;SEP&gt;North Korean youth participating in Russia's war against Ukraine have been captured as prisoners in Ukraine.</data>
