<edge source="Vladimir Putin" target="Viktor Orbán">
  <data key="d8">4.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán describes himself as a "mouse" in relation to Vladimir Putin, indicating a self-acknowledged subservient relationship and pride in this role.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán assured Vladimir Putin of unwavering support in all matters, referenced a fable to imply mutual dependence, and proposed organizing a peace summit in Budapest between Russia and the United States.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán’s political alignment with Vladimir Putin is implied to be motivated by mutual interests in undermining Western institutions and maintaining authoritarian control.&lt;SEP&gt;Vladimir Putin is described as a friend of Viktor Orbán, suggesting a strategic and ideological partnership between their regimes.</data>
