<edge source="Kremlin" target="Orbán">
  <data key="d8">4.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Orbán’s political technologists are likely linked to Kremlin structures, suggesting strategic alignment in the campaign against Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán called the Kremlin to coordinate with Vladimir Putin ahead of a planned Putin-Trump meeting in Budapest, seeking political advantage.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán’s actions protect Russian energy interests by blocking EU sanctions and pressuring Ukraine to restore oil flows, indicating alignment with Kremlin objectives.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán had a conversation with the head of the Kremlin in which he expressed willingness to become "Putin's mouse," indicating a close and friendly political stance.</data>
  <data key="d10">collaboration,communication,connection,conversation,energy dependence,political alignment,political alliance,strategic alignment</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-febe32c9e0da364a16a64ecb34a3ae7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4bd0a283b39238236a064e8afb069c87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ce845ea082895ffef253ac499ba46794</data>
