</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Slovakia">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Kremlin directly intervened in Slovak elections by instructing Hungarian officials to support SMER and Danko, aiming to install a pro-Russian coalition government.</data>
  <data key="d10">electoral manipulation,political interference</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495</data>
