</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Reading Club Budapest">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Kremlin infiltrated the Russian-language Telegram channel Reading Club Budapest with bots that posted repetitive, poorly translated comments in Hungarian to influence perception.</data>
  <data key="d10">bot activity,infiltration</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-a865b7c03998478f1296272dd37b2e83</data>
