  <data key="d13">1777934407</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Kirienko">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The bot operations linked to the Kremlin exhibit the same stylistic and tactical patterns as those associated with Kirienko, indicating a shared operational framework.</data>
  <data key="d10">coordinated tactics,operational similarity</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-a865b7c03998478f1296272dd37b2e83</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\104.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777934407</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Péter Márki-Zay">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Kremlin-linked bots targeted Péter Márki-Zay with negative, simplistic commentary in Hungarian, portraying him as weak in contrast to Viktor Orbán.</data>
  <data key="d10">criticism,disinformation</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-a865b7c03998478f1296272dd37b2e83</data>
