  <data key="d13">1777934407</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Viktor Orban">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orban established a major economic partnership with the Kremlin through the Paks II nuclear power plant deal in 2014, which solidified political ties between Hungary and Russia.</data>
  <data key="d10">diplomatic engagement,economic partnership</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\110.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777934663</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="SVR">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The SVR drafted a plan involving staged incidents in Hungary, but the Kremlin rejected it as excessive, indicating internal hesitation or strategic recalibration.</data>
  <data key="d10">internal disagreement,proposal rejection</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-8fa6adba441e776b293e92361b9880d1</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936532</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Druzhba Pipeline">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Kremlin conducted a strike on the Druzhba pipeline near Brody, causing a disruption in oil deliveries to Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d10">attack,damage</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936547</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Hungarian Government">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Hungarian Government prepared and released the transcript of Orbán’s call with the Kremlin, indicating institutional alignment with Russian interests.</data>
  <data key="d10">information sharing</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-4bd0a283b39238236a064e8afb069c87</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
