</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Peter Magyar">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Peter Magyar claimed that the false accusations against the opposition were invented by Moscow advisers operating in Hungary.&lt;SEP&gt;Peter Magyar has distanced Hungary from the Kremlin’s influence by rejecting its directives, supporting EU sanctions, and refusing to become Russia’s ally.</data>
  <data key="d10">allegation of foreign influence,diplomatic distance,non-alignment</data>
