  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Kremlin" target="Sabolch Panyi">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Sabolch Panyi observed that Kremlin and Hungarian state propaganda had jointly promoted the narrative of a planned violent action by Ukraine and the opposition.</data>
  <data key="d10">propaganda analysis</data>
