  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Орбан became the political leader of Венгрия in 1998 and initiated a national campaign to reduce crime and dismantle criminal networks.&lt;SEP&gt;Орбан was personally affected by the election results in Венгрия, where voter turnout was the highest in three decades and outcomes were less favorable.</data>
