<edge source="Slovakia" target="Robert Fico">
  <data key="d8">6.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Robert Fico serves as the Prime Minister of Slovakia, leading the government currently under threat from a referendum and parliamentary opposition.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico criticized Slovakia’s decision to transfer MiG-29 fighters to Ukraine, claiming it compromised national defense despite prior plans to replace them with F-16s.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico is under investigation by Slovakia’s General Prosecutor’s Office for alleged abuse of power and treason related to energy policy affecting Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico, as Prime Minister, represents Slovakia's position on EU sanctions.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico, as Prime Minister of Slovakia, is driving changes to the country’s electoral code to manipulate electoral outcomes in his favor.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico is accused of benefiting politically from the migration crisis in Slovakia, which was allegedly engineered to influence voter behavior in parliamentary elections.</data>
  <data key="d10">abuse of power,election,govern,governance,leadership,manipulate,policy criticism,political benefit,political leadership,reform,representation,treason investigation</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-11b9d96fc698fa7b9242168a7bad3295&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0db27d1e5bd672959a82744488e5a07&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d2e8519cd0bab60a3e52b70a90d3f0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7fe37316c34f12bcbc2eaa45277e7b90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09de750ab096b64385f95a95c7d0e5ad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cab9a94ea286a7616cc63009e8c3d5ba</data>
