  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Slovakia ordered 14 F-16 Block 70/72 fighters in 2018 to replace its aging MiG-29 fleet, with 10 delivered and four pending.&lt;SEP&gt;Slovakia is modernizing its air force by replacing MiG-29s with F-16 Block 70/72 fighters, with deliveries already underway.</data>
