  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Security Action for Europe (SAFE) fund allows EU countries to award up to 35% of contracts to UK defense companies, potentially rising to 50% if the UK joins.&lt;SEP&gt;The United Kingdom seeks to join the Security Action for Europe (SAFE) fund to increase its access to defense procurement and collaboration opportunities.</data>
