<edge source="Putin" target="Orbán">
  <data key="d8">4.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Orbán wrote a letter to Putin to inquire about Russia's reaction to the EU's potential use of frozen Russian assets for Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán and Putin had a phone conversation in which they exchanged praise and Orbán offered diplomatic assistance to Putin regarding the Russia-Ukraine war.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán and Putin described their personal friendship as strengthened since 2009 and characterized by mutual trust and availability for assistance.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán engaged in a phone call with Putin, during which he compared himself to a mouse near a lion, signaling perceived subservience to Russia.</data>
