<edge source="Robert Fico" target="Petr Pellegrini">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Robert Fico and Petr Pellegrini were political allies during the period when Slovakia ordered F-16 fighters in 2018.</data>
  <data key="d10">political alliance,shared governance</data>
