<edge source="Robert Fico" target="Viktor Orbán">
  <data key="d8">5.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán and Robert Fico are both described as latent ideological Putinists with similar positions on blocking funds for Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán and Robert Fico are alleged to be collaborating in a coordinated effort to advance Kremlin interests in Central Europe through electoral manipulation and political alignment.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán is accused of aiding Robert Fico by engineering a migration crisis to help him win elections by exploiting voter fears.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico is labeled a "mini-Orbán" due to similarities in their pro-Russian stances, but he is reluctant to fully emulate Orbán’s approach.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico's softened position on Russia is attributed to the influence of Viktor Orbán.</data>
  <data key="d10">coordination,covert support,ideological alignment,ideological proxy,political alliance,political comparison,political influence,political similarity,strategic alignment</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-0b9d4541f93fbe1abbecc6f52128db7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a55a1b2f7d86f155201f7562a7195495&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cab9a94ea286a7616cc63009e8c3d5ba&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9bcca043358a8f1b8a9a2999a79a6f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-116374b92e94e5c9f902ad74ec9408ea</data>
