<edge source="Robert Fico" target="Hungary">
  <data key="d8">3.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Robert Fico, representing Slovakia, collaborates with Hungary to restore the Druzhba oil pipeline and oppose Ukrainian attacks on Russian energy infrastructure.&lt;SEP&gt;In the previous year, Robert Fico used Hungary as a transit route to reach the May 9 Parade in Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico is perceived as a potential successor to Viktor Orbán in terms of pro-Russian policy positions within the EU, though he avoids fully assuming that role.</data>
