  <data key="d9">Robert Fico sought to fly over Latvia's territory to reach Moscow, but Latvia refused to permit the overflight.&lt;SEP&gt;Robert Fico was denied permission by Latvia to fly through its territory to reach the May 9 Parade in Moscow.&lt;SEP&gt;Latvia denied Robert Fico’s aircraft transit through its airspace, reflecting diplomatic rejection of his pro-Kremlin intentions.</data>
