<edge source="ВСУ" target="Разведос">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Разведос observes and documents the systematic targeting of Russian drone operators by ВСУ, highlighting the effectiveness of Ukrainian electronic warfare tactics.</data>
