  <data key="d9">Литва is a member of НАТО and has been officially declared a participant in the conflict by the speaker due to alleged drone launches from its territory.&lt;SEP&gt;Литва is pushing for a revision of NATO’s defense concepts, particularly advocating for an integrated air and missile defense system in response to Russian threats.</data>
