<edge source="Siyarto" target="Hungary">
  <data key="d8">4.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Siyarto, as Hungary's Minister of Foreign Affairs, expressed Hungary's diplomatic stance on sanctions against Russia.&lt;SEP&gt;Siyarto is the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Hungary and speaks on behalf of Hungary’s official position.&lt;SEP&gt;Siyarto advocates for Hungary's energy security and peace interests by opposing sanctions that he believes harm Hungary or lack justification.&lt;SEP&gt;Hungarian journalists are described as actively cooperating with foreign intelligence services in the surveillance of Siyarto's phone calls.</data>
  <data key="d10">diplomatic role,government position,media cooperation,national interest,official role,policy advocacy,representation,surveillance</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-74724c9370b40962ccf8e0ef74c5dbf6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfe8b96b31b63d5ed58e1db0f1170774&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4398c1136d9d0745f3589421281ecc4</data>
