</edge>
<edge source="Siyarto" target="Lavrov">
  <data key="d8">6.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Siyarto transmitted data to Lavrov during EU meetings, according to the Washington Post.&lt;SEP&gt;Siyarto regularly communicates with Lavrov during closed European Union meetings.&lt;SEP&gt;Siyarto engaged in direct phone conversations with Lavrov, who praised his statements and relayed requests from Russian oligarch Usmanov regarding sanctions removal.&lt;SEP&gt;Siyarto had a conversation with Lavrov, after which he made public statements regarding his actions and surveillance.&lt;SEP&gt;Lavrov instructed Siyarto to block Ukraine's EU accession negotiations and requested a document detailing the minority rights formulation, indicating direct diplomatic coordination.&lt;SEP&gt;Siyarto’s leaked phone conversations with Lavrov have created political vulnerability for Robert Fico’s government, raising fears of exposure ahead of elections.</data>
  <data key="d10">communication,conversation,coordination,diplomatic engagement,diplomatic influence,instruction,leaked communication,lobbying,political vulnerability,transmission of information</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-ba1043e375054a4f318c66342ee9ad31&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-efac8eca24c7251212c13175865647fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6610955fc2b94d091c65e9f7449d2028&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4398c1136d9d0745f3589421281ecc4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d35dd378774e42749ede8cf940deb5eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9bcca043358a8f1b8a9a2999a79a6f6</data>
