<edge source="Hungary" target="Druzhba">
  <data key="d8">3.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Hungary, through Viktor Orbán, links its support for the Ukraine credit to the restoration of Russian oil transit via the Druzhba pipeline.&lt;SEP&gt;Hungary linked its financial actions to the reopening of the Druzhba pipeline, indicating its dependence on the pipeline for future financial transfers from Ukraine.&lt;SEP&gt;After repair, the "Druzhba" pipeline is expected to resume oil deliveries to Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d10">dependency,oil supply route,policy condition,strategic interest</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-870499425ae897e4d4a7fe9c0c2b515c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21313de66f58c55ed37fed59c551bfe8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0b9d4541f93fbe1abbecc6f52128db7e</data>
