<edge source="Hungary" target="Oschadbank">
  <data key="d8">3.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Oschadbank’s armored vehicles and employees were unlawfully detained by authorities in Hungary during a routine transport.&lt;SEP&gt;Oschadbank’s cash transfers through Hungary were conducted under long-standing, agreed-upon procedures, which Hungary violated by seizing assets and detaining staff.&lt;SEP&gt;Hungarian authorities detained Oschadbank staff, confiscated funds and gold, and subjected them to inhumane treatment during border operations.</data>
