<edge source="Hungary" target="Цена голоса">
  <data key="d8">3.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The investigative report "Цена голоса" was produced by independent Hungarian media projects and revealed systemic electoral fraud within Hungary’s political system.&lt;SEP&gt;The investigation "Цена голоса" collected testimonies from 60 individuals across 14 communities in Hungary, documenting the extent of voter coercion and bribery.&lt;SEP&gt;The investigation "Цена голоса" focused on electoral misconduct occurring across multiple impoverished communities in Hungary.</data>
