  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">MO is Hungary’s sole oil distributor, using discounted Russian oil to maintain low domestic fuel prices, a policy championed by Viktor Orbán as essential for national energy security.&lt;SEP&gt;MO’s access to discounted Russian oil allows Hungary to maintain lower fuel prices than other Central European countries, a key claim in Viktor Orbán’s electoral campaigns.</data>
