<edge source="Hungary" target="2022 Hungarian Elections">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The 2022 Hungarian elections had significantly lower voter turnout rates than the current election.&lt;SEP&gt;In the 2022 Hungarian elections, 59% of voters considered Orbán’s ability to keep Hungary out of war as the most important issue.</data>
