<edge source="Hungary" target="2026 Hungarian Elections">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Hungary's electoral system was legally modified for the 2026 Hungarian Elections to favor Fidesz through district redrawing and vote compensation rules.&lt;SEP&gt;The 2026 Hungarian elections are conducted under a mixed electoral system that has been structurally biased since 2012 to favor Fidesz through gerrymandering.</data>
