<edge source="Orbán" target="Fidesz">
  <data key="d8">6.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Orbán leads the Fidesz party, which has instrumentalized the 2026 parliamentary elections as a propaganda tool to reinforce his political dominance.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán leads the political party Fidesz, which is accused of implementing the voter bribery campaign described in the investigation.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán is the leader of the Fidesz political party, which is referred to by protesters as "Dirty Fidesz".&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán is the political leader aligned with Fidesz, which executed disinformation campaigns to support his electoral narrative against Ukraine and the EU.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán leads Fidesz and has maintained political control over Hungary for 16 years, enabling the party to enact electoral reforms that consolidate its power.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán leads the Fidesz party and has used its political power to manipulate electoral boundaries and media narratives to maintain dominance.</data>
  <data key="d10">leadership,political affiliation,political alignment,political control</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-e84aa583f7aa058a2cdc38864b8c765a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26fcbf6510a404d136a66a46e0584357&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-81536517f133c3a5924be660cac3eb05&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-95251bcfc4d08a0a36c341b9a9e2da54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6bcd039eb9ab628a1ffb566a855dd2b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-867b81690ecba5bc75830acd44c39131</data>
