<edge source="Orbán" target="1956 Hungarian Uprising">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Protesters used the slogan "Russians home," originating from the 1956 Hungarian Uprising, to criticize Orbán, drawing a symbolic contrast between past resistance to Soviet forces and current political alignment.</data>
