  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Budapest, as Hungary’s capital, was proposed by Orbán as a neutral diplomatic hub for international talks.&lt;SEP&gt;Orbán offered Budapest as a potential location for a summit to mediate the Russia-Ukraine conflict.</data>
