<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Fidesz">
  <data key="d8">5.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán is the leader of the Fidesz party, which he represents in the Hungarian parliamentary elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Fidesz is the ruling political party led by Viktor Orbán, who has been Prime Minister of Hungary for 16 years.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán leads the Fidesz party, which is facing electoral decline despite his public alignment with Vladimir Putin.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán leads the Fidesz party, which has built and maintained a system of institutional control across Hungary’s government, judiciary, and media to preserve political power.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán is the leader of Fidesz and has used the party to maintain political power for 16 years through media control and electoral manipulation.</data>
  <data key="d10">institutional control,leadership,political affiliation,political control,political representation</data>
