<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Dmytro Korniienko">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Hungarian propaganda falsely accuses Dmytro Korniienko of threatening Viktor Orbán with a sword in a YouTube video, though Korniienko denies any such threat and claims the video was misrepresented.</data>
  <data key="d10">accusation,disinformation,threat</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-c4fcaac079096c59954da324c3f17538</data>
