</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Dmitriev">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Dmitriev, as Putin’s special representative, endorsed Viktor Orbán as one of the few voices of wisdom in Europe regarding the crisis.</data>
  <data key="d10">endorsement,support</data>
