<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Gáspár Orbán">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Gáspár Orbán was able to plan a strategic military mission to Chad due to his status as the son of Prime Minister Viktor Orbán, who held significant political power in Hungary.</data>
  <data key="d10">family relationship,political influence</data>
