<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Tisza">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán’s Fidesz party is trailing behind the opposition coalition Tisza in opinion polls ahead of the Hungarian parliamentary elections.&lt;SEP&gt;Viktor Orbán and Fidesz are in direct electoral competition with Tisza and its leader Péter Márki-Zay in the 2026 Hungarian elections.</data>
  <data key="d10">electoral competition,electoral rivalry,political opposition</data>
