<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Dzsózsef Orbán">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Dzsózsef Orbán, Viktor Orbán’s father, is the official owner of a large construction project in Hótvágypuszta, which is widely believed to be a front for Viktor Orbán’s hidden wealth.</data>
  <data key="d10">asset_hiding,front_company</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-49d9496e943d94ccc071cf105396b990</data>
