</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Lukashenko">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán is compared to Alexander Lukashenko as a leader who publicly portrays himself as modest and patriotic while allegedly amassing vast hidden wealth.</data>
  <data key="d10">comparison,power_narrative</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-49d9496e943d94ccc071cf105396b990</data>
