  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The large construction site in Hótvágypuszta, officially owned by Dzsózsef Orbán, is widely regarded as a concealed asset of Viktor Orbán, symbolizing his hidden wealth.</data>
  <data key="d10">hidden_asset_location</data>
