<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Katalin Novák">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Katalin Novák resigned as President of Hungary amid a scandal involving the pardon of a pedophile cover-up, which was part of the broader corruption crisis that triggered Mádiár’s public revelations.</data>
  <data key="d10">resignation,scandal_link</data>
