<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Leningrad">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The text mentions Leningrad as the alleged site where Orbán’s propaganda machine designed Mádiár as a puppet-a claim likely fictional or misstated, used to illustrate the regime’s baseless smear tactics.</data>
  <data key="d10">false_accusation,propaganda_fabrication</data>
