<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Sergey Lavrov">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán’s government engaged in discussions with Sergey Lavrov regarding sanctions, communications of which were later intercepted and revealed, undermining his claims of independence from Russian influence.</data>
  <data key="d10">intercepted communication,strategic coordination</data>
