</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Akashhadhazi">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Akashhadhazi obtained official energy certificates proving Hatvanpusta was registered as residential property, directly contradicting Viktor Orbán’s claim that it was an unfinished farm and demanding accountability.&lt;SEP&gt;Akashhadhazi challenged Viktor Orbán’s public narrative by exposing the Hatvanpusta estate and organizing protests, directly confronting Orbán’s claims of modesty and lack of personal assets.</data>
  <data key="d10">accountability demand,confrontation,evidence challenge,political opposition</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-fc1feb8e698e39594612de628b9b30f8</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
