  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="MO">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán has consistently defended MO’s access to discounted Russian oil, framing it as a personal achievement and essential to Hungary’s economic stability.</data>
  <data key="d10">policy protection,political alignment</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-fc1feb8e698e39594612de628b9b30f8</data>
