</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Druzhba">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán’s political strategy depends on the continued operation of the Druzhba pipeline to supply MO with cheap Russian oil, which he presents as vital for Hungary’s survival.</data>
  <data key="d10">policy dependency,strategic alignment</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-fc1feb8e698e39594612de628b9b30f8</data>
