</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Siyarta">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán, Prime Minister of Hungary, is implied to reward Siyarta for actions benefiting Russia, such as removing sanctions, by granting him political favor and public recognition.</data>
  <data key="d10">political patronage,reward</data>
