</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Fides">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán leads the Fides organization and has maintained its dominance in Hungarian politics for 16 years through systemic electoral manipulation.</data>
  <data key="d10">leadership,political control</data>
