  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">EU Made Simple has produced multiple videos criticizing Viktor Orbán’s impact on Hungary and the European Union, highlighting corruption and democratic erosion.</data>
  <data key="d10">criticism,media exposure</data>
