<edge source="Viktor Orbán" target="Croatia">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán’s government is accused of corrupt public spending, with infrastructure projects in Hungary costing four times more than comparable projects in Croatia.</data>
  <data key="d10">corruption,infrastructure disparity</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-1561937403235278917e112e7843f5b0</data>
