  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orbán is not directly linked to Ground News; however, the video producer (EU Made Simple) promotes Ground News as a sponsor to analyze media bias, indirectly associating the platform with the broader context of media manipulation in Hungarian politics.</data>
