  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">J.D. Vance, as Vice President of the United States, visited Budapest to endorse Viktor Orbán’s regime just before the Hungarian elections, signaling U.S. political backing.&lt;SEP&gt;J.D. Vance visited Budapest to campaign for Viktor Orbán, demonstrating official U.S. support during the election.</data>
