  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Donald Trump Jr. directly appealed to Hungarians to support Viktor Orbán, calling him a friend and ally of his father and the only European leader with a direct line to the White House.</data>
  <data key="d10">endorsement,political alliance</data>
