<edge source="Fidesz" target="Krak">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Fidesz operatives exploited drug addiction by offering Krak to vulnerable individuals in exchange for votes, leveraging their dependency for electoral gain.&lt;SEP&gt;Fidesz operatives offered Krak, a cheap and addictive drug, to addicts in poor villages as a means of influencing their voting behavior.</data>
