</edge>
<edge source="Fidesz" target="Pest">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Fidesz added two new districts in Pest to increase its electoral advantage, despite Pest having fully supported Fidesz in the previous election.</data>
  <data key="d10">electoral manipulation,gerrymandering</data>
