  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Вадим Титов, head of the new Unit for Strategic Partnership and Cooperation, is assigned to manage the Hungarian influence operation following the reorganization of Kirienko’s structure.</data>
  <data key="d10">coordination,leadership</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-ec746b6d0ff03701a4a50f1703d6bbdd</data>
