</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orban" target="1956 Uprising">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orban invokes the 1956 Uprising as a historical trauma to frame current conflicts with the European Union as struggles for national sovereignty.</data>
  <data key="d10">historical manipulation,rhetorical invocation</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3</data>
