</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orban" target="Republican Party">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orban adopted institutional and strategic elements from the Republican Party of the United States to build his political style and governance model.</data>
  <data key="d10">institutional borrowing,policy imitation</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3</data>
