<edge source="Viktor Orban" target="Silvio Berlusconi">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orban imitated Silvio Berlusconi's use of populism and football to unify the nation and consolidate political power.</data>
  <data key="d10">populist strategy,tactic imitation</data>
