</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orban" target="Felcsút">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orban built a large stadium in Felcsút to symbolize the fusion of his personal authority, politics, and sports, reinforcing his political image.</data>
  <data key="d10">power consolidation,symbolic project</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3</data>
