</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orban" target="2015 Migration Crisis">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Viktor Orban exploited the 2015 Migration Crisis to intensify conflict with the European Union and frame it as an existential threat to Hungarian sovereignty.</data>
  <data key="d10">crisis exploitation,political opportunity</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-30533205f101cc1df47f96e15592f2b3</data>
