</edge>
<edge source="Viktor Orban" target="Donald Tusk">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Donald Tusk, Prime Minister of Poland, criticized Viktor Orban's minister for the proposal involving the European Union documents.</data>
