<edge source="Soviet Union" target="1956 Hungarian Uprising">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The 1956 Hungarian Uprising was a revolt against the Soviet Union's control over Hungary, leading to the emergence of the slogan "Russians home."</data>
