<edge source="Soviet Union" target="Hungarian Uprising">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Soviet Union suppressed the Hungarian Uprising in 1956 by deploying tanks into Hungary, an act that gave symbolic weight to the protest slogan "Russians go home!"</data>
