  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Сева held authority over Игорь Король in the hierarchy and successfully prevented him from taking action against Леонид Цецюра.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol is associated with Seva through the mention of an office, though no direct relationship or interaction is described.</data>
