  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Igor Korol orchestrated an attack on Alexander Kirichanin, resulting in physical injuries, theft of his vehicle and personal belongings, and a demand for $100,000 under threat of violence against his family.</data>
  <data key="d10">assault,extortion,robbery</data>
