  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Пинтер" target="Присташ Йожеф">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Пинтер ordered the killing of Присташ Йожеф after Присташ refused to sell real estate, demonstrating a lethal resolution to a business dispute.</data>
  <data key="d10">assassination order,business conflict</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936127</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Пинтер" target="Портик Томаш">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Пинтер gave an order to Портик Томаш to eliminate Присташ Йожеф, establishing a hierarchical command structure within the criminal group.</data>
  <data key="d10">command,criminal collaboration</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936128</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Пинтер" target="Игорь">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The speaker threatened that if Игорь continued his aggression, both Игорь and Пинтер would be imprisoned.</data>
  <data key="d10">shared risk,threat</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936137</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Игорь" target="Радченко Руслан">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Радченко Руслан revealed to the speaker that Игорь was the main initiator of the attack against him.&lt;SEP&gt;Игорь fired Радченко Руслан from his group without payment after a disagreement.</data>
  <data key="d10">accusation,conflict,exposure,expulsion</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936127</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Игорь" target="Steec Nutrition">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Steec Nutrition sponsored the speaker, enabling him to live off sports supplements, which provoked Игорь’s resentment due to the speaker’s success.</data>
  <data key="d10">financial_support,sponsorship</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936127</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Игорь" target="Bucharest">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Игорь began moving his money to Bucharest, likely to avoid legal consequences or secure funds after being threatened by the speaker.</data>
  <data key="d10">asset_migration</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-bf86a2e15df18d4066d405725b001379</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936127</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Игорь" target="Саша Киричанин">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Игорь aggressively seized Саша Киричанин’s car and forced him to pay money, leading to a conflict with the speaker.</data>
  <data key="d10">aggression,financial extortion</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936134</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Игорь" target="Саша">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Игорь dismissed Саша as a mere businessman and not a true friend, despite the speaker’s childhood friendship with Саша.</data>
  <data key="d10">business association,disparagement</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936136</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Игорь" target="Октогон">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Игорь arranged a meeting through his associate at Октогон in Budapest.</data>
  <data key="d10">meeting location</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936137</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Игорь" target="BMW">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Игорь’s associates attempted to assassinate the speaker using his BMW car as the site of the attack.</data>
  <data key="d10">target of violence</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-895d4fd828feac0cdb06b4f9b74dd90d</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936137</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Могилевич" target="Король">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Могилевич delivered money to Король, who then passed it to the speaker, indicating a chain of financial transactions tied to criminal activities.</data>
  <data key="d10">criminal collaboration,money transfer</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936127</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Могилевич" target="Борош Томаш">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Борош Томаш had direct connections with Могилевич, as revealed in his testimony about illicit activities involving Орбан and others.</data>
  <data key="d10">compromat,criminal association</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936129</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Присташ Йожеф" target="Йозеф Рогоч">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Йозеф Рогоч shot and killed Присташ Йожеф near his jeep, acting as the direct perpetrator of the murder.</data>
  <data key="d10">assassination,execution</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936128</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Портик Томаш" target="Йозеф Рогоч">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Портик Томаш assigned the assassination of Присташ Йожеф to Йозеф Рогоч, who carried out the killing as a hired executor.</data>
  <data key="d10">assassination,contract assignment</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-e2abfcb6857ea1af89a247d75437a98e</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936128</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Борош Томаш" target="Пинтер Шандор">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Пинтер Шандор orchestrated the assassination of Борош Томаш to prevent him from revealing further information about criminal activities involving Орбан and others.</data>
  <data key="d10">assassination,preemptive strike</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936128</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Борош Томаш" target="Рогоч">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Рогоч detonated the car bomb planted in the Polish Fiat that killed Борош Томаш in Budapest, acting on orders from Пинтер Шандор.</data>
  <data key="d10">assassination,explosion</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936128</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Рогоч" target="Портик">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Портик transmitted instructions from Пинтер Шандор to Рогоч, enabling the assassination of Борош Томаш.</data>
  <data key="d10">command chain,information relay</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-372f1bcd0cd64c08c95815f34e60f974</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936128</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Портик" target="Шандор Пинтер">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Портик worked with Шандор Пинтер and was later imprisoned due to ties to the criminal world during the 1990s.</data>
  <data key="d10">criminal connection,professional association</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936136</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="1996" target="1997">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The period of money deliveries to Dietmar Klaud lasted from 1996 to 1997, spanning approximately three years with six to eight meetings.</data>
  <data key="d10">temporal duration</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-c338d5794d84977817897ee6bca1756e</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
