  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Шандор Пинтер" target="Сомбатхе">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Шандор Пинтер, as the Minister of the Interior, is implied to be the highest authority behind the individuals who visited the speaker in Сомбатхе to extract information.</data>
  <data key="d10">information extraction,interrogation,supervision</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936128</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Шандор Пинтер" target="Вад">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Шандор Пинтер is implied to be the highest authority behind the individuals who increased their frequency of visits to the speaker after his transfer to Вад.</data>
  <data key="d10">information extraction,interrogation,supervision</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936129</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Шандор Пинтер" target="Полиграф">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The speaker expresses strong suspicion that Шандор Пинтер would fail a polygraph test due to dishonesty, implying that Шандор Пинтер is the target of the speaker’s eventual disclosure of information.</data>
  <data key="d10">deception,manipulation,suspicion</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936129</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Шандор Пинтер" target="Шандер Пинтер">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Шандер Пинтер is a phonetic variant of Шандор Пинтер, referring to the same person, the Minister of the Interior of Hungary, as confirmed by context and speaker’s intent.</data>
  <data key="d10">identity equivalence</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936129</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Шандор Пинтер" target="Семён Могилевич">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Семён Могилевич collaborated with Шандор Пинтер, who accepted bribes to protect criminal operations, including fuel smuggling and tax evasion, conducted by Могилевич’s network.</data>
  <data key="d10">bribery,collaboration,criminal partnership</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-b163da87b444be6123192ff3f1b16be3</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936135</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Шандор Пинтер" target="Тони Дюри Визовицкий Ласлоу">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Тони Дюри Визовицкий Ласлоу worked with Шандор Пинтер and was imprisoned for connections to organized crime in the 1990s.</data>
  <data key="d10">criminal connection,professional association</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936136</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Шандор Пинтер" target="тюрьма">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Шандор Пинтер, as Minister of Interior, oversaw the prosecution and imprisonment of numerous individuals connected to the criminal underworld, including Портик and Тони Дюри Визовицкий Ласлоу.</data>
  <data key="d10">criminal crackdown,prosecution</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-6ed5a8ece2f6bc4017c8fae3014bc239</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936136</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Сомбатхе" target="Полиграф">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The polygraph test was administered to the speaker while he was detained in Сомбатхе to verify his truthfulness regarding his knowledge and past activities.</data>
  <data key="d10">interrogation,verification</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936129</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Вад" target="Полиграф">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The polygraph test was administered to the speaker while he was detained in Сомбатхе, and the results were later discussed during subsequent visits after his transfer to Вад.</data>
  <data key="d10">interrogation,verification</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-53047d8273819f991ab1b18d7532d438</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936129</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Шандер Пинтер" target="Leather Bag">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The leather bag was also delivered to Шандер Пинтер by the speaker during their frequent meetings.</data>
  <data key="d10">funding delivery</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-ac226d815cf8e5ee5f29617fff9c6877</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\134.txt</data>
