<edge source="László Kócs" target="Igor Korol">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">László Kócs had a violent confrontation with Igor Korol in a Budapest pizzeria, after which Korol attempted to recruit him by expressing admiration for his character and offering closer association.&lt;SEP&gt;Igor Korol initiated contact with László Kócs after their initial violent encounter, calling him a week later to pursue a relationship despite Kócs’s reluctance.</data>
  <data key="d10">confrontation,contact initiation,recruitment attempt,violent encounter</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-eb8a98bd952f81cd62fe86510f901918</data>
