  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Бургермейштержолт collaborated with Эзрадеш Венгри in the investigation against the speaker, but refused to engage with sensitive information about Пинтер Шандер.</data>
  <data key="d10">collaboration,investigation</data>
