<edge source="Antal Rogán" target="National Tax and Customs Administration of Hungary">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The National Tax and Customs Administration of Hungary suspended large financial transfers linked to Antal Rogán’s circle due to suspicions of money laundering.</data>
