<edge source="22 February" target="27 January">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The Russian strike on the Druzhba Pipeline on 27 January directly led to Orbán’s blockade of EU sanctions and aid to Ukraine on 22 February.</data>
  <data key="d10">causal sequence,escalation</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936550</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="22 February" target="5 March">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">The seizure of Oschadbank funds on 5 March reinforced Orbán’s earlier blockade of EU aid, creating a coordinated pattern of political pressure against Ukraine.</data>
  <data key="d10">escalation,reinforcement</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-278b7eddb3c0a5b83b47a5f27d368f14</data>
  <data key="d12">D:\ObsidianWiki\GeoSpoiler-RAG\output\normalized\Венгрия Словакия\140.txt</data>
  <data key="d13">1777936551</data>
  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="MO" target="Hatyapust">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Profits from MO are channeled through Orban-affiliated funds to finance private assets such as the Hatyapust zoo, part of his power infrastructure.</data>
  <data key="d10">funding,resource allocation</data>
  <data key="d11">chunk-a5794dba07f2f01a805d966aa0ee2115</data>
