  <data key="d14"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="CNN" target="Bulgarian Center for the Study of Democracy">
  <data key="d8">2.0</data>
  <data key="d9">CNN published an investigation conducted by the Bulgarian Center for the Study of Democracy, which analyzed Hungary’s financial ties to Russian oil through MO.&lt;SEP&gt;CNN published a research study conducted by the Bulgarian Center for the Study of Democracy on Hungary’s hidden energy costs.</data>
  <data key="d10">media dissemination,publication,research collaboration</data>
