</edge>
<edge source="Delamit Kft" target="Hatvanpusta">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Delamit Kft’s revenues are presented by the Orbán family as the financial basis for the construction and maintenance of the Hatvanpusta estate.</data>
  <data key="d10">financial link,funding source</data>
