</edge>
<edge source="Hatvanpusta" target="Mehyigorye">
  <data key="d8">1.0</data>
  <data key="d9">Journalists compared the Hatvanpusta estate to Yanukovych’s Mehyigorye residence to highlight the disparity between Viktor Orbán’s public image and the reality of his family’s wealth.</data>
  <data key="d10">comparison,symbolic contrast</data>
